var book = {
	"name": "John",
	"numChapters": 21,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26035A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26035A\"></sup>In the beginning was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26035B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26035B\"></sup>the Word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26035C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26035C\"></sup>the Word was with God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26035D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26035D\"></sup>the Word was God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was in the beginning with God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26037E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26037E\"></sup>All things were made through him, and without him was not any thing made that was made.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26038F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26038F\"></sup>In him was life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26038G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26038G\"></sup>the life was the light of men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26039H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26039H\"></sup>The light shines in the darkness, and the darkness has not overcome it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There was a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26040I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26040I\"></sup>sent from God, whose name was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26040J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26040J\"></sup>John.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He came as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26041K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26041K\"></sup>witness, to bear witness about the light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26041L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26041L\"></sup>that all might believe through him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26042M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26042M\"></sup>He was not the light, but came to bear witness about the light.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26043N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26043N\"></sup>The true light, which gives light to everyone, was coming into the world.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He was in the world, and the world was made through him, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26044O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26044O\"></sup>the world did not know him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26045P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26045P\"></sup>his own, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26045Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26045Q\"></sup>his own people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26045R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26045R\"></sup>did not receive him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But to all who did receive him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26046S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26046S\"></sup>who believed in his name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26046T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26046T\"></sup>he gave the right <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26046U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26046U\"></sup>to become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26046V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26046V\"></sup>children of God,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26047W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26047W\"></sup>were born, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26047X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26047X\"></sup>not of blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26047Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26047Y\"></sup>nor of the will of the flesh nor of the will of man, but of God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048Z\"></sup>the Word <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048AA\"></sup>became flesh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048AB\"></sup>dwelt among us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048AC\"></sup>and we have seen his glory, glory as of the only Son from the Father, full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048AD\"></sup>grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26048AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26048AE\"></sup>truth.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>(<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26049AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26049AF\"></sup>John bore witness about him, and cried out, “This was he of whom I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26049AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26049AG\"></sup>‘He who comes after me ranks before me, because he was before me.’”)",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26050AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26050AH\"></sup>his fullness we have all received, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26050AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26050AI\"></sup>grace upon grace.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26051AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26051AJ\"></sup>the law was given through Moses; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26051AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26051AK\"></sup>grace and truth came through Jesus Christ.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26052AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26052AL\"></sup>No one has ever seen God; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26052AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26052AM\"></sup>the only God, who is at the Father's side, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26052AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26052AN\"></sup>he has made him known.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26053AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26053AO\"></sup>testimony of John, when the Jews sent priests and Levites from Jerusalem to ask him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26053AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26053AP\"></sup>“Who are you?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26054AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26054AQ\"></sup>He confessed, and did not deny, but confessed, “I am not the Christ.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And they asked him, “What then? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26055AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26055AR\"></sup>Are you Elijah?” He said, “I am not.” “Are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26055AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26055AS\"></sup>the Prophet?” And he answered, “No.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So they said to him, “Who are you? We need to give an answer to those who sent us. What do you say about yourself?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He said, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26057AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26057AT\"></sup>the voice of one crying out in the wilderness, ‘Make straight the way of the Lord,’ as the prophet Isaiah said.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>(Now they had been sent from the Pharisees.)",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>They asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26059AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26059AU\"></sup>“Then why are you baptizing, if you are neither the Christ, nor Elijah, nor the Prophet?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>John answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26060AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26060AV\"></sup>“I baptize with water, but among you stands one you do not know,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26061AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26061AW\"></sup>he who comes after me, the strap of whose sandal I am not worthy to untie.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>These things took place in Bethany across the Jordan, where John was baptizing.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The next day he saw Jesus coming toward him, and said, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26063AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26063AX\"></sup>the Lamb of God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26063AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26063AY\"></sup>takes away the sin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26063AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26063AZ\"></sup>of the world!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>This is he of whom I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26064BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26064BA\"></sup>‘After me comes a man who ranks before me, because he was before me.’",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I myself did not know him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26065BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26065BB\"></sup>for this purpose I came baptizing with water, that he might be revealed to Israel.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26066BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26066BC\"></sup>bore witness: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26066BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26066BD\"></sup>“I saw the Spirit descend from heaven like a dove, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26066BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26066BE\"></sup>it remained on him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>I myself did not know him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26067BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26067BF\"></sup>he who sent me to baptize <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26067BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26067BG\"></sup>with water said to me, ‘He on whom you see the Spirit descend and remain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26067BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26067BH\"></sup>this is he who baptizes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26067BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26067BI\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And I have seen and have borne witness that this is the Son of God.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The next day again John was standing with two of his disciples,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and he looked at Jesus as he walked by and said, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26070BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26070BJ\"></sup>the Lamb of God!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>The two disciples heard him say this, and they followed Jesus.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Jesus turned and saw them following and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26072BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26072BK\"></sup>“What are you seeking?”</span> And they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26072BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26072BL\"></sup>“Rabbi” (which means Teacher), “where are you staying?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Come and you will see.”</span> So they came and saw where he was staying, and they stayed with him that day, for it was about the tenth hour.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26074BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26074BM\"></sup>One of the two who heard John speak and followed Jesus was Andrew, Simon Peter's brother.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>He first found his own brother Simon and said to him, “We have found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26075BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26075BN\"></sup>the Messiah” (which means Christ).",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>He brought him to Jesus. Jesus looked at him and said, <span class=\"woj\">“You are Simon the son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26076BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26076BO\"></sup>John. You shall be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26076BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26076BP\"></sup>Cephas”</span> (which means <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26076BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26076BQ\"></sup>Peter).",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26077BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26077BR\"></sup>The next day Jesus decided <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26077BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26077BS\"></sup>to go to Galilee. He found Philip and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow me.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26078BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26078BT\"></sup>Philip was from Bethsaida, the city of Andrew and Peter.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Philip found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26079BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26079BU\"></sup>Nathanael and said to him, “We have found him of whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26079BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26079BV\"></sup>Moses in the Law and also the prophets wrote, Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26079BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26079BW\"></sup>of Nazareth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26079BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26079BX\"></sup>the son of Joseph.”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Nathanael said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26080BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26080BY\"></sup>“Can anything good come out of Nazareth?” Philip said to him, “Come and see.”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Jesus saw Nathanael coming toward him and said of him, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26081BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26081BZ\"></sup>an Israelite indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26081CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26081CA\"></sup>in whom there is no deceit!”</span>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Nathanael said to him, “How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26082CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26082CB\"></sup>do you know me?” Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Before Philip called you, when you were under the fig tree, I saw you.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Nathanael answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26083CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26083CC\"></sup>“Rabbi, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26083CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26083CD\"></sup>you are the Son of God! You are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26083CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26083CE\"></sup>King of Israel!”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Because I said to you, ‘I saw you under the fig tree,’ do you believe? You will see greater things than these.”</span>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, you will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26085CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26085CF\"></sup>heaven opened, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26085CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26085CG\"></sup>the angels of God ascending and descending on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26085CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26085CH\"></sup>the Son of Man.”</span>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>On <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26086A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26086A\"></sup>the third day there was a wedding at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26086B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26086B\"></sup>Cana in Galilee, and the mother of Jesus was there.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Jesus also was invited to the wedding with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26087C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26087C\"></sup>his disciples.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When the wine ran out, the mother of Jesus said to him, “They have no wine.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26089D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26089D\"></sup>“Woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26089E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26089E\"></sup>what does this have to do with me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26089F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26089F\"></sup>My hour has not yet come.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>His mother said to the servants, “Do whatever he tells you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now there were six stone water jars there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26091G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26091G\"></sup>for the Jewish rites of purification, each holding twenty or thirty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26091H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26091H\"></sup>gallons.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus said to the servants, <span class=\"woj\">“Fill the jars with water.”</span> And they filled them up to the brim.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Now draw some out and take it to the master of the feast.”</span> So they took it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When the master of the feast tasted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26094I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26094I\"></sup>the water now become wine, and did not know where it came from (though the servants who had drawn the water knew), the master of the feast called the bridegroom",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and said to him, “Everyone serves the good wine first, and when people have drunk freely, then the poor wine. But you have kept the good wine until now.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>This, the first of his signs, Jesus did at Cana in Galilee, and manifested <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26096J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26096J\"></sup>his glory. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26096K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26096K\"></sup>his disciples believed in him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After this he went down to Capernaum, with his mother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26097L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26097L\"></sup>his brothers and his disciples, and they stayed there for a few days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26098M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26098M\"></sup>The Passover of the Jews was at hand, and Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26098N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26098N\"></sup>went up to Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26099O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26099O\"></sup>In the temple he found those who were selling oxen and sheep and pigeons, and the money-changers sitting there.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And making a whip of cords, he drove them all out of the temple, with the sheep and oxen. And he poured out the coins of the money-changers and overturned their tables.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he told those who sold the pigeons, <span class=\"woj\">“Take these things away; do not make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26101P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26101P\"></sup>my Father's house a house of trade.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>His disciples remembered that it was written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26102Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26102Q\"></sup>“Zeal for your house will consume me.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So the Jews said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26103R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26103R\"></sup>“What sign do you show us for doing these things?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26104S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26104S\"></sup>“Destroy this temple, and in three days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26104T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26104T\"></sup>I will raise it up.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The Jews then said, “It has taken forty-six years to build this temple, and will you raise it up in three days?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But he was speaking about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26106U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26106U\"></sup>the temple of his body.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When therefore he was raised from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26107V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26107V\"></sup>his disciples remembered that he had said this, and they believed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26107W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26107W\"></sup>the Scripture and the word that Jesus had spoken.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Now when he was in Jerusalem at the Passover Feast, many believed in his name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26108X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26108X\"></sup>when they saw the signs that he was doing.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26109Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26109Y\"></sup>on his part did not entrust himself to them, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26109Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26109Z\"></sup>he knew all people",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and needed no one to bear witness about man, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26110AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26110AA\"></sup>he himself knew what was in man."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Now there was a man of the Pharisees named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26111A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26111A\"></sup>Nicodemus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26111B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26111B\"></sup>a ruler of the Jews.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>This man came to Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26112C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26112C\"></sup>by night and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26112D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26112D\"></sup>“Rabbi, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26112E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26112E\"></sup>we know that you are a teacher come from God, for no one can do these signs that you do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26112F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26112F\"></sup>unless God is with him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless one is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26113G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26113G\"></sup>born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26113H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26113H\"></sup>again he cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26113I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26113I\"></sup>see the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Nicodemus said to him, “How can a man be born when he is old? Can he enter a second time into his mother's womb and be born?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless one is born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26115J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26115J\"></sup>of water and the Spirit, he cannot enter the kingdom of God.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26116K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26116K\"></sup>That which is born of the flesh is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26116L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26116L\"></sup>flesh, and that which is born of the Spirit is spirit.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26117M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26117M\"></sup>Do not marvel that I said to you, ‘You must be born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26117N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26117N\"></sup>again.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26118O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26118O\"></sup>The wind blows <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26118P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26118P\"></sup>where it wishes, and you hear its sound, but you do not know where it comes from or where it goes. So it is with everyone who is born of the Spirit.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Nicodemus said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26119Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26119Q\"></sup>“How can these things be?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you the teacher of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26120R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26120R\"></sup>and yet you do not understand these things?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26121S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26121S\"></sup>we speak of what we know, and bear witness to what we have seen, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26121T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26121T\"></sup>you do not receive our testimony.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If I have told you earthly things and you do not believe, how can you believe if I tell you heavenly things?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26123U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26123U\"></sup>No one has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26123V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26123V\"></sup>ascended into heaven except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26123W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26123W\"></sup>he who descended from heaven, the Son of Man.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26124X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26124X\"></sup>as Moses lifted up the serpent in the wilderness, so must the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26124Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26124Y\"></sup>be lifted up,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>that whoever believes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26125Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26125Z\"></sup>in him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26125AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26125AA\"></sup>may have eternal life.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26126AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26126AB\"></sup>God so loved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26126AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26126AC\"></sup>the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26126AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26126AD\"></sup>that he gave his only Son, that whoever believes in him should not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26126AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26126AE\"></sup>perish but have eternal life.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26127AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26127AF\"></sup>God did not send his Son into the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26127AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26127AG\"></sup>to condemn the world, but in order that the world might be saved through him.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26128AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26128AH\"></sup>Whoever believes in him is not condemned, but whoever does not believe is condemned already, because he has not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26128AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26128AI\"></sup>believed in the name of the only Son of God.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26129AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26129AJ\"></sup>And this is the judgment: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26129AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26129AK\"></sup>the light has come into the world, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26129AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26129AL\"></sup>people loved the darkness rather than the light because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26129AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26129AM\"></sup>their works were evil.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26130AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26130AN\"></sup>For everyone who does wicked things hates the light and does not come to the light, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26130AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26130AO\"></sup>lest his works should be exposed.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26131AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26131AP\"></sup>does what is true <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26131AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26131AQ\"></sup>comes to the light, so that it may be clearly seen that his works have been carried out in God.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>After this Jesus and his disciples went into the Judean countryside, and he remained there with them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26132AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26132AR\"></sup>was baptizing.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>John also was baptizing at Aenon near Salim, because water was plentiful there, and people were coming and being baptized",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>(for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26134AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26134AS\"></sup>John had not yet been put in prison).",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now a discussion arose between some of John's disciples and a Jew over <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26135AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26135AT\"></sup>purification.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they came to John and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26136AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26136AU\"></sup>“Rabbi, he who was with you across the Jordan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26136AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26136AV\"></sup>to whom you bore witness—look, he is baptizing, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26136AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26136AW\"></sup>all are going to him.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>John answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26137AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26137AX\"></sup>“A person cannot receive even one thing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26137AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26137AY\"></sup>unless it is given him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26137AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26137AZ\"></sup>from heaven.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You yourselves bear me witness, that I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26138BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26138BA\"></sup>‘I am not the Christ, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26138BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26138BB\"></sup>I have been sent before him.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26139BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26139BC\"></sup>The one who has the bride is the bridegroom. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26139BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26139BD\"></sup>The friend of the bridegroom, who stands and hears him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26139BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26139BE\"></sup>rejoices greatly at the bridegroom's voice. Therefore this joy of mine is now complete.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26140BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26140BF\"></sup>He must increase, but I must decrease.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26141BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26141BG\"></sup>He who comes from above <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26141BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26141BH\"></sup>is above all. He who is of the earth belongs to the earth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26141BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26141BI\"></sup>speaks in an earthly way. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26141BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26141BJ\"></sup>He who comes from heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26141BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26141BK\"></sup>is above all.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26142BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26142BL\"></sup>He bears witness to what he has seen and heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26142BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26142BM\"></sup>yet no one receives his testimony.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Whoever receives his testimony <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26143BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26143BN\"></sup>sets his seal to this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26143BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26143BO\"></sup>that God is true.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For he whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26144BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26144BP\"></sup>God has sent utters the words of God, for he gives the Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26144BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26144BQ\"></sup>without measure.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26145BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26145BR\"></sup>The Father loves the Son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26145BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26145BS\"></sup>has given all things into his hand.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26146BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26146BT\"></sup>Whoever believes in the Son has eternal life; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26146BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26146BU\"></sup>whoever does not obey the Son shall not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26146BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26146BV\"></sup>see life, but the wrath of God remains on him."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Now when Jesus learned that the Pharisees had heard that Jesus was making and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26147A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26147A\"></sup>baptizing more disciples than John",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>(although Jesus himself did not baptize, but only his disciples),",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>he left Judea and departed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26149B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26149B\"></sup>again for Galilee.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26150C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26150C\"></sup>And he had to pass through Samaria.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So he came to a town of Samaria called Sychar, near the field <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26151D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26151D\"></sup>that Jacob had given to his son Joseph.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jacob's well was there; so Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26152E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26152E\"></sup>wearied as he was from his journey, was sitting beside the well. It was about the sixth hour.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A woman from Samaria came to draw water. Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26153F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26153F\"></sup>“Give me a drink.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>(For his disciples had gone away into the city to buy food.)",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The Samaritan woman said to him, “How is it that you, a Jew, ask for a drink from me, a woman of Samaria?” (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26155G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26155G\"></sup>For Jews have no dealings with Samaritans.)",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus answered her, <span class=\"woj\">“If you knew the gift of God, and who it is that is saying to you, ‘Give me a drink,’ you would have asked him, and he would have given you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26156H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26156H\"></sup>living water.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The woman said to him, “Sir, you have nothing to draw water with, and the well is deep. Where do you get that living water?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26158I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26158I\"></sup>Are you greater than our father Jacob? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26158J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26158J\"></sup>He gave us the well and drank from it himself, as did his sons and his livestock.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Everyone who drinks of this water will be thirsty again,</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26160K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26160K\"></sup>whoever drinks of the water that I will give him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26160L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26160L\"></sup>will never be thirsty again. The water that I will give him will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26160M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26160M\"></sup>in him a spring of water welling up to eternal life.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The woman said to him, “Sir, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26161N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26161N\"></sup>give me this water, so that I will not be thirsty or have to come here to draw water.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26162O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26162O\"></sup>call your husband, and come here.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The woman answered him, “I have no husband.” Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“You are right in saying, ‘I have no husband’;</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for you have had five husbands, and the one you now have is not your husband. What you have said is true.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The woman said to him, “Sir, I perceive that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26165P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26165P\"></sup>you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26165Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26165Q\"></sup>a prophet.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26166R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26166R\"></sup>Our fathers worshiped on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26166S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26166S\"></sup>this mountain, but you say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26166T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26166T\"></sup>in Jerusalem is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26166U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26166U\"></sup>the place where people ought to worship.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26167V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26167V\"></sup>“Woman, believe me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26167W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26167W\"></sup>the hour is coming when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26167X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26167X\"></sup>neither on this mountain nor in Jerusalem will you worship the Father.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26168Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26168Y\"></sup>You worship what you do not know; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26168Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26168Z\"></sup>we worship what we know, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26168AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26168AA\"></sup>salvation is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26168AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26168AB\"></sup>from the Jews.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26169AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26169AC\"></sup>the hour is coming, and is now here, when the true worshipers will worship the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26169AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26169AD\"></sup>in spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26169AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26169AE\"></sup>truth, for the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26169AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26169AF\"></sup>is seeking such people to worship him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>God is spirit, and those who worship him must worship in spirit and truth.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The woman said to him, “I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26171AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26171AG\"></sup>Messiah is coming (he who is called Christ). When he comes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26171AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26171AH\"></sup>he will tell us all things.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26172AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26172AI\"></sup>“I who speak to you am he.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Just then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26173AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26173AJ\"></sup>his disciples came back. They marveled that he was talking with a woman, but no one said, “What do you seek?” or, “Why are you talking with her?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So the woman left her water jar and went away into town and said to the people,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Come, see a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26175AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26175AK\"></sup>who told me all that I ever did. Can this be the Christ?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They went out of the town and were coming to him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Meanwhile the disciples were urging him, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26177AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26177AL\"></sup>“Rabbi, eat.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I have food to eat that you do not know about.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So the disciples said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26179AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26179AM\"></sup>“Has anyone brought him something to eat?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26180AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26180AN\"></sup>“My food is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26180AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26180AO\"></sup>to do the will of him who sent me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26180AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26180AP\"></sup>to accomplish his work.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Do you not say, ‘There are yet four months, then comes the harvest’? Look, I tell you, lift up your eyes, and see that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26181AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26181AQ\"></sup>the fields are white for harvest.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Already</span> <span class=\"woj\">the one who reaps is receiving wages and gathering fruit for eternal life, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26182AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26182AR\"></sup>sower and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26182AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26182AS\"></sup>reaper <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26182AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26182AT\"></sup>may rejoice together.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For here the saying holds true, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26183AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26183AU\"></sup>‘One sows and another reaps.’</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>I sent you to reap <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26184AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26184AV\"></sup>that for which you did not labor. Others have labored, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26184AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26184AW\"></sup>and you have entered into their labor.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Many Samaritans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26185AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26185AX\"></sup>from that town believed in him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26185AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26185AY\"></sup>because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26185AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26185AZ\"></sup>the woman's testimony, “He told me all that I ever did.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So when the Samaritans came to him, they asked him to stay with them, and he stayed there two days.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And many more believed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26187BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26187BA\"></sup>because of his word.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They said to the woman, “It is no longer because of what you said that we believe, for we have heard for ourselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26188BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26188BB\"></sup>and we know that this is indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26188BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26188BC\"></sup>the Savior <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26188BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26188BD\"></sup>of the world.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26189BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26189BE\"></sup>the two days he departed for Galilee.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>(For Jesus himself had testified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26190BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26190BF\"></sup>that a prophet has no honor in his own hometown.)",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>So when he came to Galilee, the Galileans welcomed him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26191BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26191BG\"></sup>having seen all that he had done in Jerusalem at the feast. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26191BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26191BH\"></sup>they too had gone to the feast.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>So he came again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26192BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26192BI\"></sup>Cana in Galilee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26192BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26192BJ\"></sup>where he had made the water wine. And at Capernaum there was an official whose son was ill.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>When this man heard that Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26193BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26193BK\"></sup>had come from Judea to Galilee, he went to him and asked him to come down and heal his son, for he was at the point of death.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>So Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26194BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26194BL\"></sup>“Unless you see signs and wonders you will not believe.”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>The official said to him, “Sir, come down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26195BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26195BM\"></sup>before my child dies.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go; your son will live.”</span> The man believed the word that Jesus spoke to him and went on his way.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>As he was going down, his servants met him and told him that his son was recovering.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>So he asked them the hour when he began to get better, and they said to him, “Yesterday at the seventh hour the fever left him.”",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>The father knew that was the hour when Jesus had said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Your son will live.”</span> And he himself believed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26199BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26199BN\"></sup>and all his household.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26200BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26200BO\"></sup>This was now the second sign that Jesus did when he had come from Judea to Galilee."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>After this there was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26201A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26201A\"></sup>feast of the Jews, and Jesus went up to Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now there is in Jerusalem by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26202B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26202B\"></sup>the Sheep Gate a pool, in Aramaic called Bethesda, which has five roofed colonnades.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In these lay a multitude of invalids—blind, lame, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26203C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26203C\"></sup>paralyzed.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>One man was there who had been an invalid for thirty-eight years.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When Jesus saw him lying there and knew that he had already been there a long time, he said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you want to be healed?”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The sick man answered him, “Sir, I have no one to put me into the pool when the water is stirred up, and while I am going another steps down before me.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26207D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26207D\"></sup>“Get up, take up your bed, and walk.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26208E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26208E\"></sup>And at once the man was healed, and he took up his bed and walked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26208F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26208F\"></sup>Now that day was the Sabbath.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So the Jews said to the man who had been healed, “It is the Sabbath, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26209G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26209G\"></sup>it is not lawful for you to take up your bed.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But he answered them, “The man who healed me, that man said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Take up your bed, and walk.’</span>”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They asked him, “Who is the man who said to you, ‘Take up your bed and walk’?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now the man who had been healed did not know who it was, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26212H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26212H\"></sup>Jesus had withdrawn, as there was a crowd in the place.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Afterward Jesus found him in the temple and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“See, you are well! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26213I\"></sup>Sin no more, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26213J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26213J\"></sup>that nothing worse may happen to you.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The man went away and told the Jews that it was Jesus who had healed him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And this was why the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26215K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26215K\"></sup>were persecuting Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26215L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26215L\"></sup>because he was doing these things on the Sabbath.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father is working until now, and I am working.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>This was why the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26217M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26217M\"></sup>were seeking all the more to kill him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26217N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26217N\"></sup>because not only was he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26217O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26217O\"></sup>breaking the Sabbath, but he was even calling God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26217P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26217P\"></sup>his own Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26217Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26217Q\"></sup>making himself equal with God.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26218R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26218R\"></sup>the Son <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26218S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26218S\"></sup>can do nothing of his own accord, but only what he sees the Father doing. For whatever the Father does, that the Son does likewise.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26219T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26219T\"></sup>the Father loves the Son and shows him all that he himself is doing. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26219U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26219U\"></sup>greater works than these will he show him, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26219V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26219V\"></sup>you may marvel.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For as the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26220W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26220W\"></sup>raises the dead and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26220X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26220X\"></sup>gives them life, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26220Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26220Y\"></sup>also the Son gives life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26220Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26220Z\"></sup>to whom he will.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26221AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26221AA\"></sup>For the Father judges no one, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26221AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26221AB\"></sup>has given all judgment to the Son,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>that all may honor the Son, just as they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26222AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26222AC\"></sup>honor the Father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26222AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26222AD\"></sup>Whoever does not honor the Son does not honor the Father who sent him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26223AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26223AE\"></sup>whoever hears my word and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26223AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26223AF\"></sup>believes him who sent me has eternal life. He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26223AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26223AG\"></sup>does not come into judgment, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26223AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26223AH\"></sup>has passed from death to life.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26224AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26224AI\"></sup>an hour is coming, and is now here, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26224AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26224AJ\"></sup>the dead will hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26224AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26224AK\"></sup>the voice of the Son of God, and those who hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26224AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26224AL\"></sup>will live.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26225AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26225AM\"></sup>For as the Father has life in himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26225AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26225AN\"></sup>so he has granted the Son also to have life in himself.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26226AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26226AO\"></sup>has given him authority to execute judgment, because he is the Son of Man.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not marvel at this, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26227AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26227AP\"></sup>an hour is coming when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26227AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26227AQ\"></sup>all who are in the tombs will hear his voice</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>and come out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26228AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26228AR\"></sup>those who have done good to the resurrection of life, and those who have done evil to the resurrection of judgment.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26229AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26229AS\"></sup>“I can do nothing on my own. As I hear, I judge, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26229AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26229AT\"></sup>my judgment is just, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26229AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26229AU\"></sup>I seek not my own will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26229AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26229AV\"></sup>but the will of him who sent me.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26230AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26230AW\"></sup>If I alone bear witness about myself, my testimony is not true.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26231AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26231AX\"></sup>another who bears witness about me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26231AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26231AY\"></sup>I know that the testimony that he bears about me is true.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26232AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26232AZ\"></sup>You sent to John, and he has borne witness to the truth.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Not that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26233BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26233BA\"></sup>the testimony that I receive is from man, but I say these things so that you may be saved.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>He was a burning and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26234BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26234BB\"></sup>shining lamp, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26234BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26234BC\"></sup>you were willing to rejoice for a while in his light.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26235BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26235BD\"></sup>the testimony that I have is greater than that of John. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26235BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26235BE\"></sup>the works that the Father has given me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26235BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26235BF\"></sup>to accomplish, the very works that I am doing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26235BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26235BG\"></sup>bear witness about me that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26235BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26235BH\"></sup>the Father has sent me.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And the Father who sent me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26236BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26236BI\"></sup>has himself borne witness about me. His voice you have never heard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26236BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26236BJ\"></sup>his form you have never seen,</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26237BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26237BK\"></sup>you do not have his word abiding in you, for you do not believe the one whom he has sent.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26238BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26238BL\"></sup>You search the Scriptures because you think that in them you have eternal life; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26238BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26238BM\"></sup>it is they that bear witness about me,</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26239BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26239BN\"></sup>you refuse to come to me that you may have life.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26240BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26240BO\"></sup>I do not receive glory from people.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26241BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26241BP\"></sup>I know that you do not have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26241BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26241BQ\"></sup>the love of God within you.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>I have come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26242BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26242BR\"></sup>in my Father's name, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26242BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26242BS\"></sup>you do not receive me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26242BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26242BT\"></sup>If another comes in his own name, you will receive him.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>How can you believe, when you receive glory from one another and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26243BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26243BU\"></sup>do not seek the glory that comes from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26243BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26243BV\"></sup>the only God?</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Do not think that I will accuse you to the Father. There is one who accuses you: Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26244BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26244BW\"></sup>on whom you have set your hope.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>For if you believed Moses, you would believe me; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26245BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26245BX\"></sup>he wrote of me.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26246BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26246BY\"></sup>if you do not believe his writings, how will you believe my words?”</span>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>After this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26247A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26247A\"></sup>Jesus went away to the other side of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26247B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26247B\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26247C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26247C\"></sup>the Sea of Tiberias.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And a large crowd was following him, because they saw the signs that he was doing on the sick.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus went up on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26249D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26249D\"></sup>the mountain, and there he sat down with his disciples.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26250E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26250E\"></sup>the Passover, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26250F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26250F\"></sup>feast of the Jews, was at hand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26251G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26251G\"></sup>Lifting up his eyes, then, and seeing that a large crowd was coming toward him, Jesus said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26251H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26251H\"></sup>Philip, <span class=\"woj\">“Where are we to buy bread, so that these people may eat?”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said this to test him, for he himself knew what he would do.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26253I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26253I\"></sup>Philip answered him, “Two hundred denarii worth of bread would not be enough for each of them to get a little.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>One of his disciples, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26254J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26254J\"></sup>Andrew, Simon Peter's brother, said to him,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“There is a boy here who has five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26255K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26255K\"></sup>barley loaves and two fish, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26255L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26255L\"></sup>what are they for so many?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Have the people sit down.”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26256M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26256M\"></sup>Now there was much grass in the place. So the men sat down, about five thousand in number.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus then took the loaves, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26257N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26257N\"></sup>when he had given thanks, he distributed them to those who were seated. So also the fish, as much as they wanted.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when they had eaten their fill, he told his disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Gather up the leftover fragments, that nothing may be lost.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So they gathered them up and filled twelve baskets with fragments from the five barley loaves left by those who had eaten.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When the people saw the sign that he had done, they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26260O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26260O\"></sup>“This is indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26260P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26260P\"></sup>the Prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26260Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26260Q\"></sup>who is to come into the world!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26261R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26261R\"></sup>Perceiving then that they were about to come and take him by force to make him king, Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26261S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26261S\"></sup>withdrew again to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26261T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26261T\"></sup>the mountain by himself.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When evening came, his disciples went down to the sea,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>got into a boat, and started across the sea to Capernaum. It was now dark, and Jesus had not yet come to them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The sea became rough because a strong wind was blowing.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When they had rowed about three or four miles, they saw Jesus walking on the sea and coming near the boat, and they were frightened.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26266U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26266U\"></sup>But he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is I; do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then they were glad to take him into the boat, and immediately the boat was at the land to which they were going.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On the next day the crowd that remained on the other side of the sea saw that there had been only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26268V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26268V\"></sup>one boat there, and that Jesus had not entered the boat with his disciples, but that his disciples had gone away alone.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Other boats from Tiberias came near the place where they had eaten the bread after the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26269W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26269W\"></sup>had given thanks.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26270X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26270X\"></sup>So when the crowd saw that Jesus was not there, nor his disciples, they themselves got into the boats and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26270Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26270Y\"></sup>went to Capernaum, seeking Jesus.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When they found him on the other side of the sea, they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26271Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26271Z\"></sup>“Rabbi, when did you come here?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26272AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26272AA\"></sup>you are seeking me, not because you saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26272AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26272AB\"></sup>signs, but because you ate your fill of the loaves.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26273AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26273AC\"></sup>Do not work for the food that perishes, but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26273AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26273AD\"></sup>the food that endures to eternal life, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26273AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26273AE\"></sup>the Son of Man will give to you. For on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26273AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26273AF\"></sup>him God the Father has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26273AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26273AG\"></sup>set his seal.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then they said to him, “What must we do, to be doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26274AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26274AH\"></sup>the works of God?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“This is the work of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26275AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26275AI\"></sup>that you believe in him whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26275AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26275AJ\"></sup>he has sent.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26276AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26276AK\"></sup>“Then what sign do you do, that we may see and believe you? What work do you perform?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26277AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26277AL\"></sup>Our fathers ate the manna in the wilderness; as it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26277AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26277AM\"></sup>‘He gave them bread from heaven to eat.’”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Jesus then said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, it was not Moses who gave you the bread from heaven, but my Father gives you the true bread from heaven.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For the bread of God is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26279AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26279AN\"></sup>he who comes down from heaven and gives life to the world.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26280AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26280AO\"></sup>“Sir, give us this bread always.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26281AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26281AP\"></sup>“I am the bread of life; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26281AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26281AQ\"></sup>whoever comes to me shall not hunger, and whoever believes in me shall never thirst.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But I said to you that you have seen me and yet do not believe.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26283AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26283AR\"></sup>All that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26283AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26283AS\"></sup>the Father gives me will come to me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26283AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26283AT\"></sup>whoever comes to me I will never cast out.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26284AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26284AU\"></sup>I have come down from heaven, not to do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26284AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26284AV\"></sup>my own will but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26284AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26284AW\"></sup>the will of him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26284AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26284AX\"></sup>who sent me.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26285AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26285AY\"></sup>this is the will of him who sent me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26285AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26285AZ\"></sup>that I should lose nothing of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26285BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26285BA\"></sup>all that he has given me, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26285BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26285BB\"></sup>raise it up on the last day.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For this is the will of my Father, that everyone who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26286BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26286BC\"></sup>looks on the Son and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26286BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26286BD\"></sup>believes in him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26286BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26286BE\"></sup>should have eternal life, and I will raise him up on the last day.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So the Jews grumbled about him, because he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26287BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26287BF\"></sup>“I am the bread that came down from heaven.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>They said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26288BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26288BG\"></sup>“Is not this Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26288BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26288BH\"></sup>the son of Joseph, whose father and mother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26288BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26288BI\"></sup>we know? How does he now say, <span class=\"woj\">‘I have come down from heaven’</span>?”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not grumble among yourselves.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>No one can come to me unless the Father who sent me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26290BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26290BJ\"></sup>draws him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26290BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26290BK\"></sup>I will raise him up on the last day.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>It is written in the Prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26291BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26291BL\"></sup>‘And they will all be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26291BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26291BM\"></sup>taught by God.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26291BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26291BN\"></sup>Everyone who has heard and learned from the Father comes to me—</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26292BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26292BO\"></sup>not that anyone has seen the Father except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26292BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26292BP\"></sup>he who is from God; he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26292BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26292BQ\"></sup>has seen the Father.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26293BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26293BR\"></sup>whoever believes has eternal life.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26294BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26294BS\"></sup>I am the bread of life.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26295BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26295BT\"></sup>Your fathers ate the manna in the wilderness, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26295BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26295BU\"></sup>they died.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26296BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26296BV\"></sup>This is the bread that comes down from heaven, so that one may eat of it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26296BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26296BW\"></sup>and not die.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>I am the living bread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26297BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26297BX\"></sup>that came down from heaven. If anyone eats of this bread, he will live forever. And the bread that I will give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26297BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26297BY\"></sup>for the life of the world is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26297BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26297BZ\"></sup>my flesh.”</span>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>The Jews then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26298CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26298CA\"></sup>disputed among themselves, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26298CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26298CB\"></sup>“How can this man give us his flesh to eat?”",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, unless you eat the flesh of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26299CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26299CC\"></sup>the Son of Man and drink his blood, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26299CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26299CD\"></sup>have no life in you.</span>",
			"54": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Whoever feeds on my flesh and drinks my blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26300CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26300CE\"></sup>has eternal life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26300CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26300CF\"></sup>I will raise him up on the last day.</span>",
			"55": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>For my flesh is true food, and my blood is true drink.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>Whoever feeds on my flesh and drinks my blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26302CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26302CG\"></sup>abides in me, and I in him.</span>",
			"57": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26303CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26303CH\"></sup>the living Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26303CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26303CI\"></sup>sent me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26303CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26303CJ\"></sup>I live because of the Father, so whoever feeds on me, he also will live because of me.</span>",
			"58": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26304CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26304CK\"></sup>This is the bread that came down from heaven, not like the bread the fathers ate, and died. Whoever feeds on this bread will live forever.”</span>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>Jesus said these things in the synagogue, as he taught <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26305CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26305CL\"></sup>at Capernaum.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26306CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26306CM\"></sup>When many of his disciples heard it, they said, “This is a hard saying; who can listen to it?”",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>But Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26307CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26307CN\"></sup>knowing in himself that his disciples were grumbling about this, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you take offense at this?</span>",
			"62": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>Then what if you were to see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26308CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26308CO\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26308CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26308CP\"></sup>ascending to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26308CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26308CQ\"></sup>where he was before?</span>",
			"63": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26309CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26309CR\"></sup>It is the Spirit who gives life; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26309CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26309CS\"></sup>the flesh is no help at all. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26309CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26309CT\"></sup>The words that I have spoken to you are spirit and life.</span>",
			"64": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26310CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26310CU\"></sup>there are some of you who do not believe.”</span> (For Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26310CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26310CV\"></sup>knew from the beginning who those were who did not believe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26310CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26310CW\"></sup>who it was who would betray him.)",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“This is why I told you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26311CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26311CX\"></sup>that no one can come to me unless it is granted him by the Father.”</span>",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26312CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26312CY\"></sup>After this many of his disciples turned back and no longer walked with him.",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup>So Jesus said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26313CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26313CZ\"></sup>the twelve, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you want to go away as well?”</span>",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>Simon Peter answered him, “Lord, to whom shall we go? You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26314DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26314DA\"></sup>the words of eternal life,",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26315DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26315DB\"></sup>we have believed, and have come to know, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26315DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26315DC\"></sup>you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26315DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26315DD\"></sup>the Holy One of God.”",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26316DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26316DE\"></sup>“Did I not choose you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26316DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26316DF\"></sup>the twelve? And yet one of you is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26316DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26316DG\"></sup>a devil.”</span>",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>He spoke of Judas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26317DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26317DH\"></sup>the son of Simon Iscariot, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26317DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26317DI\"></sup>he, one of the twelve, was going to betray him."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After this Jesus went about in Galilee. He would not go about in Judea, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26318A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26318A\"></sup>the Jews were seeking to kill him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26319B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26319B\"></sup>the Jews' Feast of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26319C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26319C\"></sup>Booths was at hand.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26320D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26320D\"></sup>So his brothers said to him, “Leave here and go to Judea, that your disciples also may see the works you are doing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For no one works in secret if he seeks to be known openly. If you do these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26321E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26321E\"></sup>show yourself to the world.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26322F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26322F\"></sup>For not even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26322G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26322G\"></sup>his brothers believed in him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26323H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26323H\"></sup>“My time has not yet come, but your time is always here.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The world cannot hate you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26324I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26324I\"></sup>it hates me because I testify about it that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26324J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26324J\"></sup>its works are evil.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You go up to the feast. I am not going up to this feast, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26325K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26325K\"></sup>my time has not yet fully come.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After saying this, he remained in Galilee.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26327L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26327L\"></sup>his brothers had gone up to the feast, then he also went up, not publicly but in private.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26328M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26328M\"></sup>The Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26328N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26328N\"></sup>were looking for him at the feast, and saying, “Where is he?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And there was much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26329O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26329O\"></sup>muttering about him among the people. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26329P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26329P\"></sup>While some said, “He is a good man,” others said, “No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26329Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26329Q\"></sup>he is leading the people astray.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26330R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26330R\"></sup>for fear of the Jews no one spoke openly of him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>About the middle of the feast Jesus went up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26331S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26331S\"></sup>into the temple and began teaching.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The Jews therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26332T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26332T\"></sup>marveled, saying, “How is it that this man has learning, when he has never studied?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26333U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26333U\"></sup>“My teaching is not mine, but his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26333V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26333V\"></sup>who sent me.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26334W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26334W\"></sup>If anyone's will is to do God's will, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26334X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26334X\"></sup>he will know whether the teaching is from God or whether I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26334Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26334Y\"></sup>am speaking on my own authority.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The one who speaks on his own authority <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26335Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26335Z\"></sup>seeks his own glory; but the one who seeks the glory of him who sent him is true, and in him there is no falsehood.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26336AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26336AA\"></sup>Has not Moses given you the law? Yet none of you keeps the law. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26336AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26336AB\"></sup>Why do you seek to kill me?”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The crowd answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26337AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26337AC\"></sup>“You have a demon! Who is seeking to kill you?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26338AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26338AD\"></sup>one work, and you all marvel at it.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26339AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26339AE\"></sup>Moses gave you circumcision (not that it is from Moses, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26339AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26339AF\"></sup>from the fathers), and you circumcise a man on the Sabbath.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>If on the Sabbath a man receives circumcision, so that the law of Moses may not be broken, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26340AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26340AG\"></sup>are you angry with me because on the Sabbath I made a man's whole body well?</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26341AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26341AH\"></sup>Do not judge by appearances, but judge with right judgment.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Some of the people of Jerusalem therefore said, “Is not this the man whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26342AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26342AI\"></sup>they seek to kill?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And here he is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26343AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26343AJ\"></sup>speaking openly, and they say nothing to him! Can it be that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26343AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26343AK\"></sup>the authorities really know that this is the Christ?",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26344AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26344AL\"></sup>we know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26344AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26344AM\"></sup>where this man comes from, and when the Christ appears, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26344AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26344AN\"></sup>no one will know where he comes from.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So Jesus proclaimed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26345AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26345AO\"></sup>as he taught in the temple, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26345AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26345AP\"></sup>“You know me, and you know where I come from. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26345AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26345AQ\"></sup>I have not come of my own accord. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26345AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26345AR\"></sup>He who sent me is true, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26345AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26345AS\"></sup>and him you do not know.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26346AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26346AT\"></sup>I know him, for I come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26346AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26346AU\"></sup>from him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26346AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26346AV\"></sup>he sent me.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26347AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26347AW\"></sup>So they were seeking to arrest him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26347AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26347AX\"></sup>no one laid a hand on him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26347AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26347AY\"></sup>because his hour had not yet come.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26348AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26348AZ\"></sup>many of the people believed in him. They said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26348BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26348BA\"></sup>“When the Christ appears, will he do more signs than this man has done?”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The Pharisees heard the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26349BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26349BB\"></sup>muttering these things about him, and the chief priests and Pharisees sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26349BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26349BC\"></sup>officers to arrest him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Jesus then said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26350BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26350BD\"></sup>“I will be with you a little longer, and then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26350BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26350BE\"></sup>I am going to him who sent me.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26351BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26351BF\"></sup>You will seek me and you will not find me. Where I am you cannot come.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The Jews said to one another, “Where does this man intend to go that we will not find him? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26352BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26352BG\"></sup>Does he intend to go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26352BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26352BH\"></sup>the Dispersion among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26352BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26352BI\"></sup>the Greeks and teach the Greeks?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>What does he mean by saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26353BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26353BJ\"></sup>‘You will seek me and you will not find me,’</span> and, <span class=\"woj\">‘Where I am you cannot come’</span>?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26354BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26354BK\"></sup>On the last day of the feast, the great day, Jesus stood up and cried out, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26354BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26354BL\"></sup>“If anyone thirsts, let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26354BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26354BM\"></sup>come to me and drink.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Whoever believes in me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26355BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26355BN\"></sup>as the Scripture has said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26355BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26355BO\"></sup>‘Out of his heart will flow rivers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26355BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26355BP\"></sup>living water.’”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26356BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26356BQ\"></sup>this he said about the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26356BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26356BR\"></sup>whom those who believed in him were to receive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26356BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26356BS\"></sup>for as yet the Spirit had not been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26356BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26356BT\"></sup>given, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26356BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26356BU\"></sup>because Jesus was not yet glorified.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>When they heard these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26357BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26357BV\"></sup>some of the people said, “This really is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26357BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26357BW\"></sup>the Prophet.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Others said, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26358BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26358BX\"></sup>the Christ.” But some said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26358BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26358BY\"></sup>“Is the Christ to come from Galilee?",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Has not the Scripture said that the Christ comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26359BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26359BZ\"></sup>from the offspring of David, and comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26359CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26359CA\"></sup>from Bethlehem, the village <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26359CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26359CB\"></sup>where David was?”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>So there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26360CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26360CC\"></sup>a division among the people over him.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26361CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26361CD\"></sup>Some of them wanted to arrest him, but no one laid hands on him.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26362CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26362CE\"></sup>The officers then came to the chief priests and Pharisees, who said to them, “Why did you not bring him?”",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>The officers answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26363CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26363CF\"></sup>“No one ever spoke like this man!”",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The Pharisees answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26364CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26364CG\"></sup>“Have you also been deceived?",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26365CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26365CH\"></sup>Have any of the authorities or the Pharisees believed in him?",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But this crowd that does not know the law is accursed.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26367CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26367CI\"></sup>Nicodemus, who had gone to him before, and who was one of them, said to them,",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26368CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26368CJ\"></sup>“Does our law judge a man without first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26368CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26368CK\"></sup>giving him a hearing and learning what he does?”",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>They replied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26369CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26369CL\"></sup>“Are you from Galilee too? Search and see that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26369CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26369CM\"></sup>no prophet arises from Galilee.”[The earliest manuscripts do not include 7:53–8:11.]",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>[[They went each to his own house,"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum mid-paragraph\">8 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-paragraph\">1 </sup>but Jesus went to the Mount of Olives.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26372A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26372A\"></sup>Early in the morning he came again to the temple. All the people came to him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26372B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26372B\"></sup>he sat down and taught them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The scribes and the Pharisees brought a woman who had been caught in adultery, and placing her in the midst",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>they said to him, “Teacher, this woman has been caught in the act of adultery.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26375C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26375C\"></sup>in the Law, Moses commanded us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26375D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26375D\"></sup>to stone such women. So what do you say?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This they said <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26376E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26376E\"></sup>to test him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26376F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26376F\"></sup>that they might have some charge to bring against him. Jesus bent down and wrote with his finger on the ground.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And as they continued to ask him, he stood up and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26377G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26377G\"></sup>“Let him who is without sin among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26377H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26377H\"></sup>be the first to throw a stone at her.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And once more he bent down and wrote on the ground.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But when they heard it, they went away one by one, beginning with the older ones, and Jesus was left alone with the woman standing before him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus stood up and said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Woman, where are they? Has no one condemned you?”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>She said, “No one, Lord.” And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26381I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26381I\"></sup>“Neither do I condemn you; go, and from now on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26381J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26381J\"></sup>sin no more.”</span>]]",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26382K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26382K\"></sup>Again Jesus spoke to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26382L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26382L\"></sup>“I am the light of the world. Whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26382M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26382M\"></sup>follows me will not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26382N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26382N\"></sup>walk in darkness, but will have the light of life.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So the Pharisees said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26383O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26383O\"></sup>“You are bearing witness about yourself; your testimony is not true.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Even if I do bear witness about myself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26384P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26384P\"></sup>my testimony is true, for I know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26384Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26384Q\"></sup>where I came from and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26384R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26384R\"></sup>where I am going, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26384S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26384S\"></sup>you do not know where I come from or where I am going.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26385T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26385T\"></sup>You judge according to the flesh; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26385U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26385U\"></sup>I judge no one.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Yet even if I do judge, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26386V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26386V\"></sup>my judgment is true, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26386W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26386W\"></sup>it is not I alone who judge, but I and the Father who sent me.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26387X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26387X\"></sup>In your Law it is written that the testimony of two people is true.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I am the one who bears witness about myself, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26388Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26388Y\"></sup>the Father who sent me bears witness about me.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They said to him therefore, “Where is your Father?” Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26389Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26389Z\"></sup>“You know neither me nor my Father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26389AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26389AA\"></sup>If you knew me, you would know my Father also.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>These words he spoke in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26390AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26390AB\"></sup>the treasury, as he taught in the temple; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26390AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26390AC\"></sup>no one arrested him, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26390AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26390AD\"></sup>his hour had not yet come.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So he said to them again, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26391AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26391AE\"></sup>“I am going away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26391AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26391AF\"></sup>you will seek me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26391AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26391AG\"></sup>you will die in your sin. Where I am going, you cannot come.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So the Jews said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26392AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26392AH\"></sup>“Will he kill himself, since he says, <span class=\"woj\">‘Where I am going, you cannot come’</span>?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26393AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26393AI\"></sup>“You are from below; I am from above. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26393AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26393AJ\"></sup>You are of this world; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26393AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26393AK\"></sup>I am not of this world.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>I told you that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26394AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26394AL\"></sup>would die in your sins, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26394AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26394AM\"></sup>unless you believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26394AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26394AN\"></sup>I am he you will die in your sins.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So they said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26395AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26395AO\"></sup>“Who are you?” Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Just what I have been telling you from the beginning.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>I have much to say about you and much to judge, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26396AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26396AP\"></sup>he who sent me is true, and I declare <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26396AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26396AQ\"></sup>to the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26396AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26396AR\"></sup>what I have heard from him.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>They did not understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26397AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26397AS\"></sup>he had been speaking to them about the Father.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“When you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26398AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26398AT\"></sup>lifted up the Son of Man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26398AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26398AU\"></sup>then you will know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26398AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26398AV\"></sup>I am he, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26398AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26398AW\"></sup>I do nothing on my own authority, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26398AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26398AX\"></sup>speak just as the Father taught me.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26399AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26399AY\"></sup>he who sent me is with me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26399AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26399AZ\"></sup>He has not left me alone, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26399BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26399BA\"></sup>I always do the things that are pleasing to him.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>As he was saying these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26400BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26400BB\"></sup>many believed in him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So Jesus said to the Jews who had believed him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26401BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26401BC\"></sup>“If you abide in my word, you are truly my disciples,</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>and you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26402BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26402BD\"></sup>know the truth, and the truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26402BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26402BE\"></sup>will set you free.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26403BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26403BF\"></sup>“We are offspring of Abraham and have never been enslaved to anyone. How is it that you say, ‘You will become free’?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26404BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26404BG\"></sup>everyone who practices sin is a slave to sin.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26405BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26405BH\"></sup>The slave does not remain in the house forever; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26405BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26405BI\"></sup>the son remains forever.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>So if the Son sets you free, you will be free indeed.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>I know that you are offspring of Abraham; yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26407BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26407BJ\"></sup>you seek to kill me because my word finds no place in you.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26408BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26408BK\"></sup>I speak of what I have seen with my Father, and you do what you have heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26408BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26408BL\"></sup>from your father.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>They answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26409BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26409BM\"></sup>“Abraham is our father.” Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26409BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26409BN\"></sup>“If you were Abraham's children, you would be doing the works Abraham did,</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>but now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26410BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26410BO\"></sup>you seek to kill me, a man who has told you the truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26410BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26410BP\"></sup>that I heard from God. This is not what Abraham did.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>You are doing the works your father did.”</span> They said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26411BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26411BQ\"></sup>“We were not born of sexual immorality. We have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26411BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26411BR\"></sup>one Father—even God.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26412BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26412BS\"></sup>“If God were your Father, you would love me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26412BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26412BT\"></sup>I came from God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26412BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26412BU\"></sup>I am here. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26412BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26412BV\"></sup>I came not of my own accord, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26412BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26412BW\"></sup>he sent me.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26413BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26413BX\"></sup>Why do you not understand what I say? It is because you cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26413BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26413BY\"></sup>bear to hear my word.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26414BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26414BZ\"></sup>You are of your father the devil, and your will is to do your father's desires. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26414CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26414CA\"></sup>He was a murderer from the beginning, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26414CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26414CB\"></sup>does not stand in the truth, because there is no truth in him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26414CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26414CC\"></sup>When he lies, he speaks out of his own character, for he is a liar and the father of lies.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>But because I tell the truth, you do not believe me.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Which one of you convicts me of sin? If I tell the truth, why do you not believe me?</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26417CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26417CD\"></sup>Whoever is of God hears the words of God. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26417CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26417CE\"></sup>The reason why you do not hear them is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26417CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26417CF\"></sup>you are not of God.”</span>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>The Jews answered him, “Are we not right in saying that you are a Samaritan and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26418CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26418CG\"></sup>have a demon?”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“I do not have a demon, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26419CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26419CH\"></sup>I honor my Father, and you dishonor me.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26420CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26420CI\"></sup>I do not seek my own glory; there is One who seeks it, and he is the judge.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Truly, truly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26421CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26421CJ\"></sup>I say to you, if anyone keeps my word, he will never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26421CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26421CK\"></sup>see death.”</span>",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>The Jews said to him, “Now we know that you have a demon! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26422CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26422CL\"></sup>Abraham died, as did the prophets, yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26422CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26422CM\"></sup>you say, <span class=\"woj\">‘If anyone keeps my word, he will never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26422CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26422CN\"></sup>taste death.’</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26423CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26423CO\"></sup>Are you greater than our father Abraham, who died? And the prophets died! Who do you make yourself out to be?”",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26424CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26424CP\"></sup>“If I glorify myself, my glory is nothing. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26424CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26424CQ\"></sup>It is my Father who glorifies me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26424CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26424CR\"></sup>of whom you say, ‘He is our God.’</span>",
			"55": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26425CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26425CS\"></sup>you have not known him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26425CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26425CT\"></sup>I know him. If I were to say that I do not know him, I would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26425CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26425CU\"></sup>a liar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26425CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26425CV\"></sup>like you, but I do know him and I keep his word.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26426CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26426CW\"></sup>Your father Abraham <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26426CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26426CX\"></sup>rejoiced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26426CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26426CY\"></sup>that he would see my day. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26426CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26426CZ\"></sup>He saw it and was glad.”</span>",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>So the Jews said to him, “You are not yet fifty years old, and have you seen Abraham?”",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, before Abraham was, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26428DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26428DA\"></sup>I am.”</span>",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26429DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26429DB\"></sup>they picked up stones to throw at him, but Jesus hid himself and went out of the temple."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>As he passed by, he saw a man blind from birth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And his disciples asked him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26431A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26431A\"></sup>“Rabbi, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26431B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26431B\"></sup>who sinned, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26431C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26431C\"></sup>this man or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26431D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26431D\"></sup>his parents, that he was born blind?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“It was not that this man sinned, or his parents, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26432E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26432E\"></sup>that the works of God might be displayed in him.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26433F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26433F\"></sup>work the works of him who sent me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26433G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26433G\"></sup>while it is day; night is coming, when no one can work.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>As long as I am in the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26434H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26434H\"></sup>I am the light of the world.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Having said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26435I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26435I\"></sup>he spit on the ground and made mud with the saliva. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26435J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26435J\"></sup>Then he anointed the man's eyes with the mud",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, wash in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26436K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26436K\"></sup>the pool of Siloam”</span> (which means Sent). So he went and washed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26436L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26436L\"></sup>came back seeing.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The neighbors and those who had seen him before as a beggar were saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26437M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26437M\"></sup>“Is this not the man who used to sit and beg?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Some said, “It is he.” Others said, “No, but he is like him.” He kept saying, “I am the man.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So they said to him, “Then how were your eyes opened?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26440N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26440N\"></sup>“The man called Jesus made mud and anointed my eyes and said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Go to Siloam and wash.’</span> So I went and washed and received my sight.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They said to him, “Where is he?” He said, “I do not know.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They brought to the Pharisees the man who had formerly been blind.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26443O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26443O\"></sup>Now it was a Sabbath day when Jesus made the mud and opened his eyes.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26444P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26444P\"></sup>So the Pharisees again asked him how he had received his sight. And he said to them, “He put mud on my eyes, and I washed, and I see.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Some of the Pharisees said, “This man is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26445Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26445Q\"></sup>from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26445R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26445R\"></sup>for he does not keep the Sabbath.” But others said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26445S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26445S\"></sup>“How can a man who is a sinner do such signs?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26445T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26445T\"></sup>there was a division among them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So they said again to the blind man, “What do you say about him, since he has opened your eyes?” He said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26446U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26446U\"></sup>“He is a prophet.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26447V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26447V\"></sup>The Jews did not believe that he had been blind and had received his sight, until they called the parents of the man who had received his sight",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and asked them, “Is this your son, who you say was born blind? How then does he now see?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>His parents answered, “We know that this is our son and that he was born blind.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But how he now sees we do not know, nor do we know who opened his eyes. Ask him; he is of age. He will speak for himself.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>(His parents said these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26451W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26451W\"></sup>because they feared the Jews, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26451X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26451X\"></sup>the Jews had already agreed that if anyone should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26451Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26451Y\"></sup>confess Jesus to be Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26451Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26451Z\"></sup>he was to be put out of the synagogue.)",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore his parents said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26452AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26452AA\"></sup>“He is of age; ask him.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So for the second time they called the man who had been blind and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26453AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26453AB\"></sup>“Give glory to God. We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26453AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26453AC\"></sup>this man is a sinner.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He answered, “Whether he is a sinner I do not know. One thing I do know, that though I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26454AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26454AD\"></sup>was blind, now I see.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They said to him, “What did he do to you? How did he open your eyes?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>He answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26456AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26456AE\"></sup>“I have told you already, and you would not listen. Why do you want to hear it again? Do you also want to become his disciples?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And they reviled him, saying, “You are his disciple, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26457AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26457AF\"></sup>we are disciples of Moses.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>We know that God has spoken to Moses, but as for this man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26458AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26458AG\"></sup>we do not know where he comes from.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The man answered, “Why, this is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26459AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26459AH\"></sup>an amazing thing! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26459AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26459AI\"></sup>You do not know where he comes from, and yet he opened my eyes.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26460AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26460AJ\"></sup>God does not listen to sinners, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26460AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26460AK\"></sup>if anyone is a worshiper of God and does his will, God listens to him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Never since the world began has it been heard that anyone opened the eyes of a man born blind.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26462AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26462AL\"></sup>If this man were not from God, he could do nothing.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>They answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26463AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26463AM\"></sup>“You were born in utter sin, and would you teach us?” And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26463AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26463AN\"></sup>cast him out.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus heard that they had cast him out, and having found him he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you believe in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26464AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26464AO\"></sup>the Son of Man?”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>He answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26465AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26465AP\"></sup>“And who is he, sir, that I may believe in him?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“You have seen him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26466AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26466AQ\"></sup>it is he who is speaking to you.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>He said, “Lord, I believe,” and he worshiped him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26468AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26468AR\"></sup>“For judgment I came into this world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26468AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26468AS\"></sup>that those who do not see may see, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26468AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26468AT\"></sup>those who see may become blind.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Some of the Pharisees near him heard these things, and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26469AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26469AU\"></sup>“Are we also blind?”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“If you were blind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26470AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26470AV\"></sup>you would have no guilt; but now that you say, ‘We see,’ your guilt remains.</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>“Truly, truly, I say to you, he who does not enter the sheepfold by the door but climbs in by another way, that man is a thief and a robber.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But he who enters by the door is the shepherd of the sheep.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To him the gatekeeper opens. The sheep hear his voice, and he calls his own sheep by name and leads them out.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When he has brought out all his own, he goes before them, and the sheep follow him, for they know his voice.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26475A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26475A\"></sup>A stranger they will not follow, but they will flee from him, for they do not know the voice of strangers.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>This figure of speech Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26476B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26476B\"></sup>used with them, but they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26476C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26476C\"></sup>did not understand what he was saying to them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So Jesus again said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26477D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26477D\"></sup>I am the door of the sheep.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>All who came before me are thieves and robbers, but the sheep did not listen to them.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I am the door. If anyone enters by me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26479E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26479E\"></sup>he will be saved and will go in and out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26479F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26479F\"></sup>find pasture.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The thief comes only to steal and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26480G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26480G\"></sup>kill and destroy. I came that they may have life and have it abundantly.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26481H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26481H\"></sup>I am the good shepherd. The good shepherd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26481I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26481I\"></sup>lays down his life for the sheep.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26482J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26482J\"></sup>a hired hand and not a shepherd, who does not own the sheep, sees the wolf coming and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26482K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26482K\"></sup>leaves the sheep and flees, and the wolf snatches them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26482L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26482L\"></sup>scatters them.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He flees because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26483M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26483M\"></sup>he is a hired hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26483N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26483N\"></sup>cares nothing for the sheep.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26484O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26484O\"></sup>I am the good shepherd. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26484P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26484P\"></sup>I know my own and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26484Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26484Q\"></sup>my own know me,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26485R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26485R\"></sup>just as the Father knows me and I know the Father; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26485S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26485S\"></sup>I lay down my life for the sheep.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26486T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26486T\"></sup>I have other sheep that are not of this fold. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26486U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26486U\"></sup>I must bring them also, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26486V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26486V\"></sup>they will listen to my voice. So there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26486W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26486W\"></sup>one flock, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26486X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26486X\"></sup>one shepherd.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26487Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26487Y\"></sup>For this reason the Father loves me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26487Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26487Z\"></sup>because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26487AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26487AA\"></sup>I lay down my life that I may take it up again.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26488AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26488AB\"></sup>No one takes it from me, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26488AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26488AC\"></sup>I lay it down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26488AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26488AD\"></sup>of my own accord. I have authority to lay it down, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26488AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26488AE\"></sup>I have authority to take it up again. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26488AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26488AF\"></sup>This charge I have received from my Father.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26489AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26489AG\"></sup>There was again a division among the Jews because of these words.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Many of them said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26490AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26490AH\"></sup>“He has a demon, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26490AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26490AI\"></sup>is insane; why listen to him?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Others said, “These are not the words of one who is oppressed by a demon. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26491AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26491AJ\"></sup>Can a demon open the eyes of the blind?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>At that time the Feast of Dedication took place at Jerusalem. It was winter,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and Jesus was walking in the temple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26493AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26493AK\"></sup>in the colonnade of Solomon.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So the Jews gathered around him and said to him, “How long will you keep us in suspense? If you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26494AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26494AL\"></sup>the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26494AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26494AM\"></sup>tell us plainly.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I told you, and you do not believe. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26495AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26495AN\"></sup>The works that I do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26495AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26495AO\"></sup>in my Father's name bear witness about me,</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26496AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26496AP\"></sup>you do not believe because you are not among my sheep.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26497AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26497AQ\"></sup>My sheep hear my voice, and I know them, and they follow me.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26498AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26498AR\"></sup>I give them eternal life, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26498AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26498AS\"></sup>they will never perish, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26498AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26498AT\"></sup>no one will snatch them out of my hand.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>My Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26499AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26499AU\"></sup>who has given them to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26499AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26499AV\"></sup>is greater than all, and no one is able to snatch them out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26499AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26499AW\"></sup>the Father's hand.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26500AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26500AX\"></sup>I and the Father are one.”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26501AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26501AY\"></sup>The Jews picked up stones again to stone him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“I have shown you many good works from the Father; for which of them are you going to stone me?”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The Jews answered him, “It is not for a good work that we are going to stone you but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26503AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26503AZ\"></sup>for blasphemy, because you, being a man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26503BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26503BA\"></sup>make yourself God.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Is it not written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26504BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26504BB\"></sup>your Law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26504BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26504BC\"></sup>‘I said, you are gods’?</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>If he called them gods to whom the word of God came—and Scripture cannot be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26505BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26505BD\"></sup>broken—</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>do you say of him whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26506BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26506BE\"></sup>the Father consecrated and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26506BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26506BF\"></sup>sent into the world, ‘You are blaspheming,’ because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26506BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26506BG\"></sup>I said, ‘I am the Son of God’?</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26507BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26507BH\"></sup>If I am not doing the works of my Father, then do not believe me;</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>but if I do them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26508BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26508BI\"></sup>even though you do not believe me, believe the works, that you may know and understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26508BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26508BJ\"></sup>the Father is in me and I am in the Father.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26509BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26509BK\"></sup>Again they sought to arrest him, but he escaped from their hands.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>He went away again across the Jordan to the place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26510BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26510BL\"></sup>where John had been baptizing at first, and there he remained.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And many came to him. And they said, “John did no sign, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26511BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26511BM\"></sup>everything that John said about this man was true.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26512BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26512BN\"></sup>many believed in him there."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now a certain man was ill, Lazarus of Bethany, the village of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26513A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26513A\"></sup>Mary and her sister Martha.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26514B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26514B\"></sup>It was Mary who anointed the Lord with ointment and wiped his feet with her hair, whose brother Lazarus was ill.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So the sisters sent to him, saying, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26515C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26515C\"></sup>he whom you love is ill.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But when Jesus heard it he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26516D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26516D\"></sup>“This illness does not lead to death. It is for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26516E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26516E\"></sup>the glory of God, so that the Son of God may be glorified through it.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26517F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26517F\"></sup>Jesus loved Martha and her sister and Lazarus.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So, when he heard that Lazarus was ill, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26518G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26518G\"></sup>he stayed two days longer in the place where he was.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then after this he said to the disciples, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26519H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26519H\"></sup>“Let us go to Judea again.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The disciples said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26520I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26520I\"></sup>“Rabbi, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26520J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26520J\"></sup>the Jews were just now seeking to stone you, and are you going there again?”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26521K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26521K\"></sup>“Are there not twelve hours in the day? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26521L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26521L\"></sup>If anyone walks in the day, he does not stumble, because he sees the light of this world.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26522M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26522M\"></sup>if anyone walks in the night, he stumbles, because the light is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26522N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26522N\"></sup>in him.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>After saying these things, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Our friend Lazarus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26523O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26523O\"></sup>has fallen asleep, but I go to awaken him.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The disciples said to him, “Lord, if he has fallen asleep, he will recover.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now Jesus had spoken of his death, but they thought that he meant taking rest in sleep.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Jesus told them plainly, <span class=\"woj\">“Lazarus has died,</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and for your sake I am glad that I was not there, so that you may believe. But let us go to him.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26528P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26528P\"></sup>So Thomas, called the Twin, said to his fellow disciples, “Let us also go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26528Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26528Q\"></sup>that we may die with him.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now when Jesus came, he found that Lazarus had already been in the tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26529R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26529R\"></sup>four days.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Bethany was near Jerusalem, about two miles off,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and many of the Jews had come to Martha and Mary <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26531S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26531S\"></sup>to console them concerning their brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26532T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26532T\"></sup>So when Martha heard that Jesus was coming, she went and met him, but Mary remained seated in the house.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Martha said to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26533U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26533U\"></sup>Jesus, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26533V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26533V\"></sup>if you had been here, my brother would not have died.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But even now I know that whatever you ask from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26534W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26534W\"></sup>God will give you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Your brother will rise again.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26536X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26536X\"></sup>Martha said to him, “I know that he will rise again in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26536Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26536Y\"></sup>the resurrection on the last day.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26537Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26537Z\"></sup>“I am the resurrection and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26537AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26537AA\"></sup>the life. Whoever believes in me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26537AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26537AB\"></sup>though he die, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26537AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26537AC\"></sup>yet shall he live,</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and everyone who lives and believes in me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26538AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26538AD\"></sup>shall never die. Do you believe this?”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>She said to him, “Yes, Lord; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26539AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26539AE\"></sup>I believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26539AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26539AF\"></sup>you are the Christ, the Son of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26539AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26539AG\"></sup>who is coming into the world.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When she had said this, she went and called her sister Mary, saying in private, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26540AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26540AH\"></sup>“The Teacher is here and is calling for you.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And when she heard it, she rose quickly and went to him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now Jesus had not yet come into the village, but was still in the place where Martha had met him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26543AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26543AI\"></sup>who were with her in the house, consoling her, saw Mary rise quickly and go out, they followed her, supposing that she was going to the tomb to weep there.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now when Mary came to where Jesus was and saw him, she fell at his feet, saying to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26544AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26544AJ\"></sup>“Lord, if you had been here, my brother would not have died.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When Jesus saw her weeping, and the Jews who had come with her also weeping, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26545AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26545AK\"></sup>was deeply moved in his spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26545AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26545AL\"></sup>greatly troubled.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Where have you laid him?”</span> They said to him, “Lord, come and see.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26547AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26547AM\"></sup>Jesus wept.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>So the Jews said, “See <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26548AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26548AN\"></sup>how he loved him!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But some of them said, “Could not he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26549AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26549AO\"></sup>who opened the eyes of the blind man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26549AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26549AP\"></sup>also have kept this man from dying?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26550AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26550AQ\"></sup>deeply moved again, came to the tomb. It was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26550AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26550AR\"></sup>a cave, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26550AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26550AS\"></sup>a stone lay against it.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take away the stone.”</span> Martha, the sister of the dead man, said to him, “Lord, by this time there will be an odor, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26551AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26551AT\"></sup>he has been dead four days.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26552AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26552AU\"></sup>“Did I not tell you that if you believed you would see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26552AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26552AV\"></sup>the glory of God?”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So they took away the stone. And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26553AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26553AW\"></sup>lifted up his eyes and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Father, I thank you that you have heard me.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26554AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26554AX\"></sup>I knew that you always hear me, but I said this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26554AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26554AY\"></sup>on account of the people standing around, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26554AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26554AZ\"></sup>that they may believe that you sent me.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>When he had said these things, he cried out with a loud voice, <span class=\"woj\">“Lazarus, come out.”</span>",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26556BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26556BA\"></sup>The man who had died came out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26556BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26556BB\"></sup>his hands and feet bound with linen strips, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26556BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26556BC\"></sup>his face wrapped with a cloth. Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Unbind him, and let him go.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26557BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26557BD\"></sup>Many of the Jews therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26557BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26557BE\"></sup>who had come with Mary and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26557BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26557BF\"></sup>had seen what he did, believed in him,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>but some of them went to the Pharisees and told them what Jesus had done.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>So the chief priests and the Pharisees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26559BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26559BG\"></sup>gathered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26559BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26559BH\"></sup>the council and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26559BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26559BI\"></sup>“What are we to do? For this man performs many signs.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>If we let him go on like this, everyone will believe in him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26560BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26560BJ\"></sup>the Romans will come and take away both our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26560BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26560BK\"></sup>place and our nation.”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26561BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26561BL\"></sup>Caiaphas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26561BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26561BM\"></sup>who was high priest that year, said to them, “You know nothing at all.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Nor do you understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26562BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26562BN\"></sup>it is better for you that one man should die for the people, not that the whole nation should perish.”",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>He did not say this of his own accord, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26563BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26563BO\"></sup>being high priest that year <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26563BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26563BP\"></sup>he prophesied that Jesus would die for the nation,",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26564BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26564BQ\"></sup>not for the nation only, but also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26564BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26564BR\"></sup>to gather into one the children of God who are scattered abroad.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>So from that day on they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26565BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26565BS\"></sup>made plans to put him to death.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Jesus therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26566BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26566BT\"></sup>no longer walked openly among the Jews, but went from there to the region near the wilderness, to a town called Ephraim, and there he stayed with the disciples.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26567BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26567BU\"></sup>the Passover of the Jews was at hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26567BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26567BV\"></sup>many went up from the country to Jerusalem before the Passover <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26567BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26567BW\"></sup>to purify themselves.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26568BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26568BX\"></sup>They were looking for Jesus and saying to one another as they stood in the temple, “What do you think? That he will not come to the feast at all?”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>Now the chief priests and the Pharisees had given orders that if anyone knew where he was, he should let them know, so that they might arrest him."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Six days before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26570A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26570A\"></sup>the Passover, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26570B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26570B\"></sup>Jesus therefore came to Bethany, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26570C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26570C\"></sup>where Lazarus was, whom Jesus had raised from the dead.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So they gave a dinner for him there. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26571D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26571D\"></sup>Martha served, and Lazarus was one of those reclining with him at table.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26572E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26572E\"></sup>Mary therefore took a pound of expensive ointment made from pure nard, and anointed the feet of Jesus and wiped his feet with her hair. The house was filled with the fragrance of the perfume.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But Judas Iscariot, one of his disciples (he who was about to betray him), said,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Why was this ointment not sold for three hundred denarii and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26574F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26574F\"></sup>given to the poor?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He said this, not because he cared about the poor, but because he was a thief, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26575G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26575G\"></sup>having charge of the moneybag he used to help himself to what was put into it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Leave her alone, so that she may keep it for the day of my burial.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the poor you always have with you, but you do not always have me.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When the large crowd of the Jews learned that Jesus was there, they came, not only on account of him but also to see Lazarus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26578H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26578H\"></sup>whom he had raised from the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26579I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26579I\"></sup>So the chief priests made plans to put Lazarus to death as well,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26580J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26580J\"></sup>on account of him many of the Jews were going away and believing in Jesus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26581K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26581K\"></sup>the large crowd that had come to the feast heard that Jesus was coming to Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So they took branches of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26582L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26582L\"></sup>palm trees and went out to meet him, crying out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26582M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26582M\"></sup>“Hosanna! Blessed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26582N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26582N\"></sup>he who comes in the name of the Lord, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26582O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26582O\"></sup>the King of Israel!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And Jesus found a young donkey and sat on it, just as it is written,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26584P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26584P\"></sup>“Fear not, daughter of Zion;behold, your king is coming,sitting on a donkey's colt!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26585Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26585Q\"></sup>His disciples did not understand these things at first, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26585R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26585R\"></sup>when Jesus was glorified, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26585S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26585S\"></sup>they remembered that these things had been written about him and had been done to him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26586T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26586T\"></sup>The crowd that had been with him when he called Lazarus out of the tomb and raised him from the dead continued to bear witness.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The reason why the crowd went to meet him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26587U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26587U\"></sup>was that they heard he had done this sign.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So the Pharisees said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26588V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26588V\"></sup>“You see that you are gaining nothing. Look, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26588W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26588W\"></sup>the world has gone after him.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26589X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26589X\"></sup>among those who went up to worship at the feast were some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26589Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26589Y\"></sup>Greeks.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So these came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26590Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26590Z\"></sup>Philip, who was from Bethsaida in Galilee, and asked him, “Sir, we wish to see Jesus.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Philip went and told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26591AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26591AA\"></sup>Andrew; Andrew and Philip went and told Jesus.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26592AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26592AB\"></sup>“The hour has come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26592AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26592AC\"></sup>for the Son of Man to be glorified.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26593AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26593AD\"></sup>unless a grain of wheat falls into the earth and dies, it remains alone; but if it dies, it bears much fruit.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26594AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26594AE\"></sup>Whoever loves his life loses it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26594AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26594AF\"></sup>whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26594AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26594AG\"></sup>hates his life in this world will keep it for eternal life.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If anyone serves me, he must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26595AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26595AH\"></sup>follow me; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26595AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26595AI\"></sup>where I am, there will my servant be also. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26595AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26595AJ\"></sup>If anyone serves me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26595AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26595AK\"></sup>the Father will honor him.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26596AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26596AL\"></sup>“Now is my soul troubled. And what shall I say? ‘Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26596AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26596AM\"></sup>save me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26596AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26596AN\"></sup>this hour’? But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26596AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26596AO\"></sup>for this purpose I have come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26596AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26596AP\"></sup>this hour.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Father, glorify your name.”</span> Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26597AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26597AQ\"></sup>a voice came from heaven: “I have glorified it, and I will glorify it again.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>The crowd that stood there and heard it said that it had thundered. Others said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26598AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26598AR\"></sup>“An angel has spoken to him.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26599AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26599AS\"></sup>“This voice has come for your sake, not mine.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26600AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26600AT\"></sup>Now is the judgment of this world; now will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26600AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26600AU\"></sup>the ruler of this world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26600AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26600AV\"></sup>be cast out.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26601AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26601AW\"></sup>when I am lifted up from the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26601AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26601AX\"></sup>will draw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26601AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26601AY\"></sup>all people to myself.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He said this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26602AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26602AZ\"></sup>to show by what kind of death he was going to die.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>So the crowd answered him, “We have heard from the Law that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26603BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26603BA\"></sup>the Christ remains forever. How can you say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26603BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26603BB\"></sup>the Son of Man must be lifted up? Who is this Son of Man?”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>So Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26604BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26604BC\"></sup>“The light is among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26604BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26604BD\"></sup>for a little while longer. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26604BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26604BE\"></sup>Walk while you have the light, lest darkness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26604BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26604BF\"></sup>overtake you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26604BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26604BG\"></sup>The one who walks in the darkness does not know where he is going.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>While you have the light, believe in the light, that you may become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26605BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26605BH\"></sup>sons of light.”</span>When Jesus had said these things, he departed and hid himself from them.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Though he had done so many signs before them, they still did not believe in him,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26607BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26607BI\"></sup>so that the word spoken by the prophet Isaiah might be fulfilled:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26607BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26607BJ\"></sup>“Lord, who has believed what he heard from us,and to whom has the arm of the Lord been revealed?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Therefore they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26608BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26608BK\"></sup>could not believe. For again Isaiah said,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26609BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26609BL\"></sup>“He has blinded their eyesand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26609BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26609BM\"></sup>hardened their heart,lest they see with their eyes,and understand with their heart, and turn,and I would heal them.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Isaiah said these things because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26610BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26610BN\"></sup>he saw his glory and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26610BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26610BO\"></sup>spoke of him.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Nevertheless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26611BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26611BP\"></sup>many even of the authorities believed in him, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26611BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26611BQ\"></sup>for fear of the Pharisees they did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26611BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26611BR\"></sup>confess it, so that they would not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26611BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26611BS\"></sup>put out of the synagogue;",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26612BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26612BT\"></sup>for they loved the glory that comes from man more than the glory that comes from God.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And Jesus cried out and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26613BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26613BU\"></sup>“Whoever believes in me, believes not in me but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26613BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26613BV\"></sup>in him who sent me.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26614BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26614BW\"></sup>whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26614BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26614BX\"></sup>sees me sees him who sent me.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26615BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26615BY\"></sup>I have come into the world as light, so that whoever believes in me may not remain in darkness.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26616BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26616BZ\"></sup>hears my words and does not keep them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26616CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26616CA\"></sup>I do not judge him; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26616CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26616CB\"></sup>I did not come to judge the world but to save the world.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26617CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26617CC\"></sup>The one who rejects me and does not receive my words has a judge; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26617CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26617CD\"></sup>the word that I have spoken will judge him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26617CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26617CE\"></sup>on the last day.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26618CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26618CF\"></sup>I have not spoken on my own authority, but the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26618CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26618CG\"></sup>who sent me has himself given me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26618CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26618CH\"></sup>a commandment—what to say and what to speak.</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And I know that his commandment is eternal life. What I say, therefore, I say as the Father has told me.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620A\"></sup>before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620B\"></sup>the Feast of the Passover, when Jesus knew that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620C\"></sup>his hour had come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620D\"></sup>to depart out of this world to the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620E\"></sup>having loved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26620F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26620F\"></sup>his own who were in the world, he loved them to the end.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>During supper, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26621G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26621G\"></sup>the devil had already put it into the heart of Judas Iscariot, Simon's son, to betray him,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus, knowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26622H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26622H\"></sup>that the Father had given all things into his hands, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26622I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26622I\"></sup>he had come from God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26622J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26622J\"></sup>was going back to God,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>rose from supper. He laid aside his outer garments, and taking a towel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26623K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26623K\"></sup>tied it around his waist.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26624L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26624L\"></sup>poured water into a basin and began to wash the disciples' feet and to wipe them with the towel that was wrapped around him.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He came to Simon Peter, who said to him, “Lord, do you wash my feet?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26626M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26626M\"></sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“What I am doing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26626N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26626N\"></sup>you do not understand now, but afterward you will understand.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26627O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26627O\"></sup>Peter said to him, “You shall never wash my feet.” Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26627P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26627P\"></sup>“If I do not wash you, you have no share with me.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Simon Peter said to him, “Lord, not my feet only but also my hands and my head!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“The one who has bathed does not need to wash, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26629Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26629Q\"></sup>except for his feet, but is completely clean. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26629R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26629R\"></sup>you are clean, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26629S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26629S\"></sup>but not every one of you.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26630T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26630T\"></sup>For he knew who was to betray him; that was why he said, <span class=\"woj\">“Not all of you are clean.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When he had washed their feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26631U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26631U\"></sup>put on his outer garments and resumed his place, he said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26631V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26631V\"></sup>“Do you understand what I have done to you?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26632W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26632W\"></sup>You call me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26632X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26632X\"></sup>Teacher and Lord, and you are right, for so I am.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If I then, your Lord and Teacher, have washed your feet, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26633Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26633Y\"></sup>you also ought to wash one another's feet.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For I have given you an example, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26634Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26634Z\"></sup>that you also should do just as I have done to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26635AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26635AA\"></sup>a servant is not greater than his master, nor is a messenger greater than the one who sent him.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If you know these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26636AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26636AB\"></sup>blessed are you if you do them.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26637AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26637AC\"></sup>I am not speaking of all of you; I know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26637AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26637AD\"></sup>whom I have chosen. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26637AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26637AE\"></sup>the Scripture will be fulfilled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26637AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26637AF\"></sup>‘He who ate my bread has lifted his heel against me.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26638AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26638AG\"></sup>I am telling you this now, before it takes place, that when it does take place you may believe that I am he.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26639AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26639AH\"></sup>whoever receives the one I send receives me, and whoever receives me receives the one who sent me.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>After saying these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26640AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26640AI\"></sup>Jesus was troubled in his spirit, and testified, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26640AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26640AJ\"></sup>“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26640AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26640AK\"></sup>one of you will betray me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26641AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26641AL\"></sup>The disciples looked at one another, uncertain of whom he spoke.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26642AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26642AM\"></sup>One of his disciples, whom Jesus loved, was reclining at table <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26642AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26642AN\"></sup>at Jesus' side,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>so Simon Peter motioned to him to ask Jesus of whom he was speaking.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26644AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26644AO\"></sup>So that disciple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26644AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26644AP\"></sup>leaning back against Jesus, said to him, “Lord, who is it?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26645AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26645AQ\"></sup>“It is he to whom I will give this morsel of bread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26645AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26645AR\"></sup>when I have dipped it.”</span> So when he had dipped the morsel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26645AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26645AS\"></sup>he gave it to Judas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26645AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26645AT\"></sup>the son of Simon Iscariot.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then after he had taken the morsel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26646AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26646AU\"></sup>Satan entered into him. Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26646AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26646AV\"></sup>“What you are going to do, do quickly.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Now no one at the table knew why he said this to him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Some thought that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26648AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26648AW\"></sup>because Judas had the moneybag, Jesus was telling him, “Buy what we need <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26648AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26648AX\"></sup>for the feast,” or that he should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26648AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26648AY\"></sup>give something to the poor.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So, after receiving the morsel of bread, he immediately went out. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26649AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26649AZ\"></sup>And it was night.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When he had gone out, Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26650BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26650BA\"></sup>“Now is the Son of Man glorified, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26650BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26650BB\"></sup>God is glorified in him.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If God is glorified in him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26651BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26651BC\"></sup>God will also glorify him in himself, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26651BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26651BD\"></sup>glorify him at once.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Little children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26652BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26652BE\"></sup>yet a little while I am with you. You will seek me, and just <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26652BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26652BF\"></sup>as I said to the Jews, so now I also say to you, ‘Where I am going you cannot come.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26653BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26653BG\"></sup>A new commandment <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26653BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26653BH\"></sup>I give to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26653BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26653BI\"></sup>that you love one another: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26653BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26653BJ\"></sup>just as I have loved you, you also are to love one another.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26654BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26654BK\"></sup>By this all people will know that you are my disciples, if you have love for one another.”</span>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Simon Peter said to him, “Lord, where are you going?” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26655BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26655BL\"></sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“Where I am going <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26655BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26655BM\"></sup>you cannot follow me now, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26655BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26655BN\"></sup>but you will follow afterward.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26656BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26656BO\"></sup>Peter said to him, “Lord, why can I not follow you now? I will lay down my life for you.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Will you lay down your life for me? Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26657BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26657BP\"></sup>the rooster will not crow till you have denied me three times.</span>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26658A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26658A\"></sup>“Let not your hearts be troubled. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26658B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26658B\"></sup>Believe in God; believe also in me.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26659C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26659C\"></sup>my Father's house are many rooms. If it were not so, would I have told you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26659D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26659D\"></sup>I go to prepare a place for you?</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And if I go and prepare a place for you, I will come again and will take you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26660E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26660E\"></sup>to myself, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26660F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26660F\"></sup>where I am you may be also.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And you know the way to where I am going.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26662G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26662G\"></sup>Thomas said to him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26662H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26662H\"></sup>we do not know where you are going. How can we know the way?”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26663I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26663I\"></sup>the way, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26663J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26663J\"></sup>the truth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26663K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26663K\"></sup>the life. No one comes to the Father except through me.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26664L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26664L\"></sup>If you had known me, you would have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26664M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26664M\"></sup>known my Father also. From now on you do know him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26664N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26664N\"></sup>have seen him.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26665O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26665O\"></sup>Philip said to him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26665P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26665P\"></sup>show us the Father, and it is enough for us.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Have I been with you so long, and you still do not know me, Philip? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26666Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26666Q\"></sup>Whoever has seen me has seen the Father. How can you say, ‘Show us the Father’?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do you not believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26667R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26667R\"></sup>I am in the Father and the Father is in me? The words that I say to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26667S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26667S\"></sup>I do not speak on my own authority, but the Father who dwells in me does his works.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Believe me that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26668T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26668T\"></sup>I am in the Father and the Father is in me, or else <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26668U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26668U\"></sup>believe on account of the works themselves.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26669V\"></sup>whoever believes in me will also do the works that I do; and greater works than these will he do, because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26669W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26669W\"></sup>am going to the Father.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26670X\"></sup>Whatever you ask in my name, this I will do, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26670Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26670Y\"></sup>the Father may be glorified in the Son.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26671Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26671Z\"></sup>If you ask me anything in my name, I will do it.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26672AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26672AA\"></sup>“If you love me, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26672AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26672AB\"></sup>keep my commandments.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And I will ask the Father, and he will give you another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26673AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26673AC\"></sup>Helper, to be with you forever,</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26674AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26674AD\"></sup>the Spirit of truth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26674AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26674AE\"></sup>whom the world cannot receive, because it neither sees him nor knows him. You know him, for he dwells with you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26674AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26674AF\"></sup>will be in you.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I will not leave you as orphans; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26675AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26675AG\"></sup>I will come to you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26676AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26676AH\"></sup>Yet a little while and the world will see me no more, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26676AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26676AI\"></sup>you will see me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26676AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26676AJ\"></sup>Because I live, you also will live.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26677AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26677AK\"></sup>In that day you will know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26677AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26677AL\"></sup>I am in my Father, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26677AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26677AM\"></sup>you in me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26677AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26677AN\"></sup>I in you.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26678AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26678AO\"></sup>Whoever has my commandments and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26678AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26678AP\"></sup>keeps them, he it is who loves me. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26678AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26678AQ\"></sup>he who loves me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26678AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26678AR\"></sup>will be loved by my Father, and I will love him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26678AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26678AS\"></sup>manifest myself to him.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26679AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26679AT\"></sup>Judas (not Iscariot) said to him, “Lord, how is it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26679AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26679AU\"></sup>that you will manifest yourself to us, and not to the world?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26680AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26680AV\"></sup>“If anyone loves me, he will keep my word, and my Father will love him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26680AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26680AW\"></sup>we will come to him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26680AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26680AX\"></sup>make our home with him.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Whoever does not love me does not keep my words. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26681AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26681AY\"></sup>the word that you hear is not mine but the Father's who sent me.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“These things I have spoken to you while I am still with you.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26683AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26683AZ\"></sup>Helper, the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26683BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26683BA\"></sup>whom the Father will send in my name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26683BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26683BB\"></sup>he will teach you all things and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26683BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26683BC\"></sup>bring to your remembrance all that I have said to you.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26684BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26684BD\"></sup>Peace I leave with you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26684BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26684BE\"></sup>my peace I give to you. Not as the world gives do I give to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26684BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26684BF\"></sup>Let not your hearts be troubled, neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26684BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26684BG\"></sup>let them be afraid.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26685BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26685BH\"></sup>You heard me say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26685BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26685BI\"></sup>‘I am going away, and I will come to you.’ If you loved me, you would have rejoiced, because I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26685BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26685BJ\"></sup>am going to the Father, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26685BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26685BK\"></sup>the Father is greater than I.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26686BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26686BL\"></sup>now I have told you before it takes place, so that when it does take place you may believe.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>I will no longer talk much with you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26687BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26687BM\"></sup>the ruler of this world is coming. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26687BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26687BN\"></sup>He has no claim on me,</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>but I do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26688BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26688BO\"></sup>as the Father has commanded me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26688BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26688BP\"></sup>so that the world may know that I love the Father. Rise, let us go from here.</span>"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>“I am the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26689A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26689A\"></sup>true vine, and my Father is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26689B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26689B\"></sup>the vinedresser.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26690C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26690C\"></sup>Every branch in me that does not bear fruit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26690D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26690D\"></sup>he takes away, and every branch that does bear fruit he prunes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26690E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26690E\"></sup>that it may bear more fruit.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Already <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26691F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26691F\"></sup>you are clean <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26691G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26691G\"></sup>because of the word that I have spoken to you.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26692H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26692H\"></sup>Abide <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26692I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26692I\"></sup>in me, and I in you. As the branch cannot bear fruit by itself, unless it abides in the vine, neither can you, unless you abide in me.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I am the vine; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26693J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26693J\"></sup>you are the branches. Whoever abides in me and I in him, he it is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26693K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26693K\"></sup>bears much fruit, for apart from me you can do nothing.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>If anyone does not abide in me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26694L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26694L\"></sup>he is thrown away like a branch and withers; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26694M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26694M\"></sup>and the branches are gathered, thrown into the fire, and burned.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26695N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26695N\"></sup>you abide in me, and my words abide in you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26695O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26695O\"></sup>ask whatever you wish, and it will be done for you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26696P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26696P\"></sup>By this my Father is glorified, that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26696Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26696Q\"></sup>bear much fruit and so prove to be my disciples.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26697R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26697R\"></sup>As the Father has loved me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26697S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26697S\"></sup>so have I loved you. Abide in my love.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26698T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26698T\"></sup>If you keep my commandments, you will abide in my love, just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26698U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26698U\"></sup>I have kept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26698V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26698V\"></sup>my Father's commandments and abide in his love.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>These things I have spoken to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26699W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26699W\"></sup>that my joy may be in you, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26699X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26699X\"></sup>your joy may be full.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26700Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26700Y\"></sup>“This is my commandment, that you love one another as I have loved you.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26701Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26701Z\"></sup>Greater love has no one than this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26701AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26701AA\"></sup>that someone lay down his life for his friends.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26702AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26702AB\"></sup>my friends <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26702AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26702AC\"></sup>if you do what I command you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26703AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26703AD\"></sup>No longer do I call you servants, for the servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26703AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26703AE\"></sup>does not know what his master is doing; but I have called you friends, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26703AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26703AF\"></sup>all that I have heard from my Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26703AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26703AG\"></sup>I have made known to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You did not choose me, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26704AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26704AH\"></sup>I chose you and appointed you that you should go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26704AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26704AI\"></sup>bear fruit and that your fruit should abide, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26704AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26704AJ\"></sup>whatever you ask the Father in my name, he may give it to you.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>These things I command you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26705AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26705AK\"></sup>so that you will love one another.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26706AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26706AL\"></sup>“If the world hates you, know that it has hated me before it hated you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26707AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26707AM\"></sup>If you were of the world, the world would love you as its own; but because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26707AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26707AN\"></sup>you are not of the world, but I chose you out of the world, therefore the world hates you.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Remember the word that I said to you: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26708AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26708AO\"></sup>‘A servant is not greater than his master.’ If they persecuted me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26708AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26708AP\"></sup>they will also persecute you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26708AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26708AQ\"></sup>If they kept my word, they will also keep yours.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26709AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26709AR\"></sup>all these things they will do to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26709AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26709AS\"></sup>on account of my name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26709AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26709AT\"></sup>because they do not know him who sent me.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If I had not come and spoken to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26710AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26710AU\"></sup>they would not have been guilty of sin, but now they have no excuse for their sin.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26711AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26711AV\"></sup>Whoever hates me hates my Father also.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26712AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26712AW\"></sup>If I had not done among them the works that no one else did, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26712AX\"></sup>they would not be guilty of sin, but now they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26712AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26712AY\"></sup>seen and hated both me and my Father.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26713AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26713AZ\"></sup>the word that is written in their Law must be fulfilled: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26713BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26713BA\"></sup>‘They hated me without a cause.’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26714BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26714BB\"></sup>when the Helper comes, whom I will send to you from the Father, the Spirit of truth, who proceeds from the Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26714BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26714BC\"></sup>he will bear witness about me.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26715BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26715BD\"></sup>you also will bear witness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26715BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26715BE\"></sup>because you have been with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26715BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26715BF\"></sup>from the beginning.</span>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>“I have said all these things to you to keep you from falling away.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26717A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26717A\"></sup>They will put you out of the synagogues. Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26717B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26717B\"></sup>the hour is coming when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26717C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26717C\"></sup>whoever kills you will think he is offering service to God.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they will do these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26718D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26718D\"></sup>because they have not known the Father, nor me.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26719E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26719E\"></sup>I have said these things to you, that when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26719F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26719F\"></sup>their hour comes you may remember that I told them to you.</span><span class=\"woj\">“I did not say these things to you from the beginning, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26719G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26719G\"></sup>because I was with you.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26720H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26720H\"></sup>I am going to him who sent me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26720I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26720I\"></sup>none of you asks me, ‘Where are you going?’</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But because I have said these things to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26721J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26721J\"></sup>sorrow has filled your heart.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Nevertheless, I tell you the truth: it is to your advantage that I go away, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26722K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26722K\"></sup>if I do not go away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26722L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26722L\"></sup>the Helper will not come to you. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26722M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26722M\"></sup>if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26722N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26722N\"></sup>I go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26722O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26722O\"></sup>I will send him to you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26723P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26723P\"></sup>And when he comes, he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26723Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26723Q\"></sup>convict the world concerning sin and righteousness and judgment:</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>concerning sin, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26724R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26724R\"></sup>because they do not believe in me;</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26725S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26725S\"></sup>concerning righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26725T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26725T\"></sup>because I go to the Father, and you will see me no longer;</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26726U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26726U\"></sup>concerning judgment, because the ruler of this world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26726V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26726V\"></sup>is judged.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I still have many things to say to you, but you cannot bear them now.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26728W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26728W\"></sup>the Spirit of truth comes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26728X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26728X\"></sup>he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26728Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26728Y\"></sup>guide you into all the truth, for he will not speak on his own authority, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26728Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26728Z\"></sup>whatever he hears he will speak, and he will declare to you the things that are to come.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26729AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26729AA\"></sup>glorify me, for he will take what is mine and declare it to you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26730AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26730AB\"></sup>All that the Father has is mine; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26730AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26730AC\"></sup>therefore I said that he will take what is mine and declare it to you.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26731AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26731AD\"></sup>“A little while, and you will see me no longer; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26731AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26731AE\"></sup>again a little while, and you will see me.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26732AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26732AF\"></sup>some of his disciples said to one another, “What is this that he says to us, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26732AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26732AG\"></sup>‘A little while, and you will not see me, and again a little while, and you will see me’;</span> and, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26732AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26732AH\"></sup>‘because I am going to the Father’</span>?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So they were saying, “What does he mean by <span class=\"woj\">‘a little while’</span>? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26733AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26733AI\"></sup>We do not know what he is talking about.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26734AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26734AJ\"></sup>Jesus knew that they wanted to ask him, so he said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Is this what you are asking yourselves, what I meant by saying, ‘A little while and you will not see me, and again a little while and you will see me’?</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26735AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26735AK\"></sup>you will weep and lament, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26735AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26735AL\"></sup>the world will rejoice. You will be sorrowful, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26735AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26735AM\"></sup>your sorrow will turn into joy.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26736AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26736AN\"></sup>When a woman is giving birth, she has sorrow because her hour has come, but when she has delivered the baby, she no longer remembers the anguish, for joy that a human being has been born into the world.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26737AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26737AO\"></sup>So also you have sorrow now, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26737AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26737AP\"></sup>I will see you again, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26737AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26737AQ\"></sup>your hearts will rejoice, and no one will take your joy from you.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26738AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26738AR\"></sup>In that day you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26738AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26738AS\"></sup>ask nothing of me. Truly, truly, I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26738AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26738AT\"></sup>whatever you ask of the Father in my name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26738AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26738AU\"></sup>he will give it to you.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Until now you have asked nothing in my name. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26739AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26739AV\"></sup>Ask, and you will receive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26739AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26739AW\"></sup>that your joy may be full.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I have said these things to you in figures of speech. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26740AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26740AX\"></sup>The hour is coming when I will no longer speak to you in figures of speech but will tell you plainly about the Father.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>In that day you will ask in my name, and I do not say to you that I will ask the Father on your behalf;</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26742AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26742AY\"></sup>for the Father himself loves you, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26742AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26742AZ\"></sup>you have loved me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26742BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26742BA\"></sup>have believed that I came from God.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26743BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26743BB\"></sup>I came from the Father and have come into the world, and now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26743BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26743BC\"></sup>I am leaving the world and going to the Father.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>His disciples said, “Ah, now you are speaking plainly and not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26744BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26744BD\"></sup>using figurative speech!",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now we know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26745BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26745BE\"></sup>you know all things and do not need anyone to question you; this is why we believe that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26745BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26745BF\"></sup>you came from God.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you now believe?</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26747BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26747BG\"></sup>the hour is coming, indeed it has come, when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26747BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26747BH\"></sup>you will be scattered, each to his own home, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26747BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26747BI\"></sup>will leave me alone. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26747BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26747BJ\"></sup>Yet I am not alone, for the Father is with me.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>I have said these things to you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26748BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26748BK\"></sup>in me you may have peace. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26748BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26748BL\"></sup>In the world you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26748BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26748BM\"></sup>tribulation. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26748BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26748BN\"></sup>take heart; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26748BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26748BO\"></sup>I have overcome the world.”</span>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>When Jesus had spoken these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26749A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26749A\"></sup>he lifted up his eyes to heaven, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26749B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26749B\"></sup>the hour has come; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26749C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26749C\"></sup>glorify your Son that the Son may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26749D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26749D\"></sup>glorify you,</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26750E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26750E\"></sup>you have given him authority over all flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26750F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26750F\"></sup>to give eternal life to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26750G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26750G\"></sup>whom you have given him.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26751H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26751H\"></sup>And this is eternal life, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26751I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26751I\"></sup>that they know you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26751J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26751J\"></sup>the only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26751K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26751K\"></sup>true God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26751L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26751L\"></sup>Jesus Christ whom you have sent.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26752M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26752M\"></sup>glorified you on earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26752N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26752N\"></sup>having accomplished the work that you gave me to do.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And now, Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26753O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26753O\"></sup>glorify me in your own presence with the glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26753P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26753P\"></sup>that I had with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26753Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26753Q\"></sup>before the world existed.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26754R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26754R\"></sup>“I have manifested your name to the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26754S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26754S\"></sup>whom you gave me out of the world. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26754T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26754T\"></sup>Yours they were, and you gave them to me, and they have kept your word.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now they know that everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26755U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26755U\"></sup>that you have given me is from you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For I have given them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26756V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26756V\"></sup>the words that you gave me, and they have received them and have come to know in truth that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26756W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26756W\"></sup>I came from you; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26756X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26756X\"></sup>they have believed that you sent me.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I am praying for them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26757Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26757Y\"></sup>I am not praying for the world but for those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26757Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26757Z\"></sup>whom you have given me, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26757AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26757AA\"></sup>they are yours.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26758AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26758AB\"></sup>All mine are yours, and yours are mine, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26758AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26758AC\"></sup>I am glorified in them.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And I am no longer in the world, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AD\"></sup>they are in the world, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AE\"></sup>I am coming to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AF\"></sup>Holy Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AG\"></sup>keep them in your name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AH\"></sup>which you have given me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AI\"></sup>that they may be one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26759AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26759AJ\"></sup>even as we are one.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26760AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26760AK\"></sup>While I was with them, I kept them in your name, which you have given me. I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26760AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26760AL\"></sup>guarded them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26760AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26760AM\"></sup>not one of them has been lost except <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26760AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26760AN\"></sup>the son of destruction, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26760AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26760AO\"></sup>that the Scripture might be fulfilled.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26761AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26761AP\"></sup>I am coming to you, and these things I speak in the world, that they may have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26761AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26761AQ\"></sup>my joy fulfilled in themselves.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26762AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26762AR\"></sup>I have given them your word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26762AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26762AS\"></sup>the world has hated them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26762AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26762AT\"></sup>because they are not of the world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26762AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26762AU\"></sup>just as I am not of the world.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26763AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26763AV\"></sup>do not ask that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26763AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26763AW\"></sup>take them out of the world, but that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26763AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26763AX\"></sup>keep them from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26763AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26763AY\"></sup>the evil one.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26764AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26764AZ\"></sup>They are not of the world, just as I am not of the world.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26765BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26765BA\"></sup>Sanctify them in the truth; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26765BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26765BB\"></sup>your word is truth.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26766BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26766BC\"></sup>As you sent me into the world, so I have sent them into the world.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26767BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26767BD\"></sup>for their sake <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26767BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26767BE\"></sup>I consecrate myself, that they also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26767BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26767BF\"></sup>may be sanctified in truth.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“I do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26768BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26768BG\"></sup>ask for these only, but also for those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26768BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26768BH\"></sup>who will believe in me through their word,</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26769BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26769BI\"></sup>that they may all be one, just as you, Father, are in me, and I in you, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26769BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26769BJ\"></sup>they also may be in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26769BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26769BK\"></sup>us, so that the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26769BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26769BL\"></sup>may believe that you have sent me.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26770BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26770BM\"></sup>The glory that you have given me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26770BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26770BN\"></sup>I have given to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26770BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26770BO\"></sup>that they may be one even as we are one,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26771BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26771BP\"></sup>I in them and you in me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26771BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26771BQ\"></sup>that they may become perfectly one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26771BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26771BR\"></sup>so that the world may know that you sent me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26771BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26771BS\"></sup>loved them even as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26771BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26771BT\"></sup>you loved me.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Father, I desire that they also, whom you have given me, may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26772BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26772BU\"></sup>with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26772BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26772BV\"></sup>where I am, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26772BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26772BW\"></sup>to see my glory that you have given me because you loved me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26772BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26772BX\"></sup>before the foundation of the world.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26773BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26773BY\"></sup>O righteous Father, even though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26773BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26773BZ\"></sup>the world does not know you, I know you, and these know that you have sent me.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26774CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26774CA\"></sup>I made known to them your name, and I will continue to make it known, that the love <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26774CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26774CB\"></sup>with which you have loved me may be in them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26774CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26774CC\"></sup>I in them.”</span>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>When Jesus had spoken these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26775A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26775A\"></sup>he went out with his disciples across <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26775B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26775B\"></sup>the brook Kidron, where there was a garden, which he and his disciples entered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now Judas, who betrayed him, also knew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26776C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26776C\"></sup>the place, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26776D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26776D\"></sup>Jesus often met there with his disciples.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26777E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26777E\"></sup>So Judas, having procured a band of soldiers and some officers from the chief priests and the Pharisees, went there with lanterns and torches and weapons.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26778F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26778F\"></sup>knowing all that would happen to him, came forward and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26778G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26778G\"></sup>“Whom do you seek?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They answered him, “Jesus of Nazareth.” Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I am he.”</span> Judas, who betrayed him, was standing with them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26780H\"></sup>When Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I am he,”</span> they drew back and fell to the ground.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So he asked them again, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26781I\"></sup>“Whom do you seek?”</span> And they said, “Jesus of Nazareth.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“I told you that I am he. So, if you seek me, let these men go.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26783J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26783J\"></sup>This was to fulfill the word that he had spoken: <span class=\"woj\">“Of those whom you gave me I have lost not one.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Simon Peter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26784K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26784K\"></sup>having a sword, drew it and struck the high priest's servant and cut off his right ear. (The servant's name was Malchus.)",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So Jesus said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“Put your sword into its sheath; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26785L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26785L\"></sup>shall I not drink the cup that the Father has given me?”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So the band of soldiers and their captain and the officers of the Jews arrested Jesus and bound him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>First they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26787M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26787M\"></sup>led him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26787N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26787N\"></sup>Annas, for he was the father-in-law of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26787O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26787O\"></sup>Caiaphas, who was high priest that year.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>It was Caiaphas who had advised the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26788P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26788P\"></sup>that it would be expedient that one man should die for the people.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26789Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26789Q\"></sup>Simon Peter followed Jesus, and so did another disciple. Since that disciple was known to the high priest, he entered with Jesus into the courtyard of the high priest,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26790R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26790R\"></sup>but Peter stood outside at the door. So the other disciple, who was known to the high priest, went out and spoke to the servant girl who kept watch at the door, and brought Peter in.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26791S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26791S\"></sup>The servant girl at the door said to Peter, “You also are not one of this man's disciples, are you?” He said, “I am not.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now the servants and officers had made a charcoal fire, because it was cold, and they were standing and warming themselves. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26792T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26792T\"></sup>Peter also was with them, standing and warming himself.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26793U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26793U\"></sup>The high priest then questioned Jesus about his disciples and his teaching.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“I have spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26794V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26794V\"></sup>openly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26794W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26794W\"></sup>to the world. I have always taught in synagogues and in the temple, where all Jews come together. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26794X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26794X\"></sup>I have said nothing in secret.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Why do you ask me? Ask those who have heard me what I said to them; they know what I said.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When he had said these things, one of the officers standing by struck Jesus with his hand, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26796Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26796Y\"></sup>“Is that how you answer the high priest?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\">“If what I said is wrong, bear witness about the wrong; but if what I said is right, why do you strike me?”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26798Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26798Z\"></sup>Annas then sent him bound to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26798AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26798AA\"></sup>Caiaphas the high priest.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26799AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26799AB\"></sup>Now Simon Peter was standing and warming himself. So they said to him, “You also are not one of his disciples, are you?” He denied it and said, “I am not.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>One of the servants of the high priest, a relative of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26800AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26800AC\"></sup>the man whose ear Peter had cut off, asked, “Did I not see you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26800AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26800AD\"></sup>in the garden with him?”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Peter again denied it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26801AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26801AE\"></sup>at once a rooster crowed.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26802AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26802AF\"></sup>Then they led Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26802AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26802AG\"></sup>from the house of Caiaphas to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26802AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26802AH\"></sup>the governor's headquarters. It was early morning. They themselves did not enter the governor's headquarters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26802AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26802AI\"></sup>so that they would not be defiled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26802AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26802AJ\"></sup>but could eat the Passover.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26803AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26803AK\"></sup>So Pilate went outside to them and said, “What accusation do you bring against this man?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>They answered him, “If this man were not doing evil, we would not have delivered him over to you.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Pilate said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26805AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26805AL\"></sup>“Take him yourselves and judge him by your own law.” The Jews said to him, “It is not lawful for us to put anyone to death.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26806AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26806AM\"></sup>This was to fulfill the word that Jesus had spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26806AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26806AN\"></sup>to show by what kind of death he was going to die.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26807AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26807AO\"></sup>So Pilate entered his headquarters again and called Jesus and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26807AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26807AP\"></sup>“Are you the King of the Jews?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you say this of your own accord, or did others say it to you about me?”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Pilate answered, “Am I a Jew? Your own nation and the chief priests have delivered you over to me. What have you done?”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26810AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26810AQ\"></sup>“My kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26810AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26810AR\"></sup>is not of this world. If my kingdom were of this world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26810AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26810AS\"></sup>my servants would have been fighting, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26810AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26810AT\"></sup>I might not be delivered over to the Jews. But my kingdom is not from the world.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then Pilate said to him, “So you are a king?” Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AU\"></sup>“You say that I am a king. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AV\"></sup>For this purpose I was born and for this purpose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AW\"></sup>I have come into the world—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AX\"></sup>to bear witness to the truth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AY\"></sup>Everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811AZ\"></sup>of the truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26811BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26811BA\"></sup>listens to my voice.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Pilate said to him, “What is truth?”After he had said this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26812BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26812BB\"></sup>he went back outside to the Jews and told them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26812BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26812BC\"></sup>“I find no guilt in him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26813BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26813BD\"></sup>But you have a custom that I should release one man for you at the Passover. So do you want me to release to you the King of the Jews?”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>They cried out again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26814BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26814BE\"></sup>“Not this man, but Barabbas!” Now Barabbas was a robber."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>Then Pilate took Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26815A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26815A\"></sup>flogged him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26816B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26816B\"></sup>And the soldiers twisted together a crown of thorns and put it on his head and arrayed him in a purple robe.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They came up to him, saying, “Hail, King of the Jews!” and struck him with their hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Pilate went out again and said to them, “See, I am bringing him out to you that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26818C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26818C\"></sup>I find no guilt in him.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So Jesus came out, wearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26819D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26819D\"></sup>the crown of thorns and the purple robe. Pilate said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26819E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26819E\"></sup>“Behold the man!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When the chief priests and the officers saw him, they cried out, “Crucify him, crucify him!” Pilate said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26820F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26820F\"></sup>“Take him yourselves and crucify him, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26820G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26820G\"></sup>I find no guilt in him.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The Jews answered him, “We have a law, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26821H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26821H\"></sup>according to that law he ought to die because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26821I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26821I\"></sup>he has made himself the Son of God.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>When Pilate heard this statement, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26822J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26822J\"></sup>he was even more afraid.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26823K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26823K\"></sup>He entered his headquarters again and said to Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26823L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26823L\"></sup>“Where are you from?” But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26823M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26823M\"></sup>Jesus gave him no answer.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So Pilate said to him, “You will not speak to me? Do you not know that I have authority to release you and authority to crucify you?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus answered him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26825N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26825N\"></sup>“You would have no authority over me at all unless it had been given you from above. Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26825O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26825O\"></sup>he who delivered me over to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26825P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26825P\"></sup>has the greater sin.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>From then on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26826Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26826Q\"></sup>Pilate sought to release him, but the Jews cried out, “If you release this man, you are not Caesar's friend. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26826R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26826R\"></sup>Everyone who makes himself a king opposes Caesar.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So when Pilate heard these words, he brought Jesus out and sat down on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26827S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26827S\"></sup>the judgment seat at a place called The Stone Pavement, and in Aramaic Gabbatha.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26828T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26828T\"></sup>the day of Preparation of the Passover. It was about the sixth hour. He said to the Jews, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26828U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26828U\"></sup>“Behold your King!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They cried out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26829V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26829V\"></sup>“Away with him, away with him, crucify him!” Pilate said to them, “Shall I crucify your King?” The chief priests answered, “We have no king but Caesar.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26830W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26830W\"></sup>So he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26830X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26830X\"></sup>delivered him over to them to be crucified.So they took Jesus,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26831Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26831Y\"></sup>he went out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26831Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26831Z\"></sup>bearing his own cross, to the place called The Place of a Skull, which in Aramaic is called Golgotha.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26832AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26832AA\"></sup>There they crucified him, and with him two others, one on either side, and Jesus between them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Pilate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26833AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26833AB\"></sup>also wrote an inscription and put it on the cross. It read, “Jesus of Nazareth, the King of the Jews.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Many of the Jews read this inscription, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26834AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26834AC\"></sup>the place where Jesus was crucified was near the city, and it was written in Aramaic, in Latin, and in Greek.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So the chief priests of the Jews said to Pilate, “Do not write, ‘The King of the Jews,’ but rather, ‘This man said, I am King of the Jews.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Pilate answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26836AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26836AD\"></sup>“What I have written I have written.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26837AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26837AE\"></sup>When the soldiers had crucified Jesus, they took his garments and divided them into four parts, one part for each soldier; also his tunic. But the tunic was seamless, woven in one piece from top to bottom,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>so they said to one another, “Let us not tear it, but cast lots for it to see whose it shall be.” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26838AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26838AF\"></sup>This was to fulfill the Scripture which says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26838AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26838AG\"></sup>“They divided my garments among them,and for my clothing they cast lots.”So the soldiers did these things,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26839AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26839AH\"></sup>but standing by the cross of Jesus were his mother and his mother's sister, Mary the wife of Clopas, and Mary Magdalene.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When Jesus saw his mother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26840AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26840AI\"></sup>the disciple whom he loved standing nearby, he said to his mother, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26840AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26840AJ\"></sup>“Woman, behold, your son!”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then he said to the disciple, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, your mother!”</span> And from that hour the disciple took her to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26841AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26841AK\"></sup>his own home.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>After this, Jesus, knowing that all was now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26842AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26842AL\"></sup>finished, said (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26842AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26842AM\"></sup>to fulfill the Scripture), <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26842AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26842AN\"></sup>“I thirst.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>A jar full of sour wine stood there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26843AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26843AO\"></sup>so they put a sponge full of the sour wine on a hyssop branch and held it to his mouth.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>When Jesus had received the sour wine, he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26844AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26844AP\"></sup>“It is finished,”</span> and he bowed his head and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26844AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26844AQ\"></sup>gave up his spirit.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Since it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26845AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26845AR\"></sup>the day of Preparation, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26845AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26845AS\"></sup>so that the bodies would not remain on the cross on the Sabbath (for that Sabbath was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26845AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26845AT\"></sup>a high day), the Jews asked Pilate that their legs might be broken and that they might be taken away.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>So the soldiers came and broke the legs of the first, and of the other <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26846AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26846AU\"></sup>who had been crucified with him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But when they came to Jesus and saw that he was already dead, they did not break his legs.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But one of the soldiers pierced his side with a spear, and at once there came out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26848AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26848AV\"></sup>blood and water.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26849AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26849AW\"></sup>He who saw it has borne witness—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26849AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26849AX\"></sup>his testimony is true, and he knows that he is telling the truth—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26849AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26849AY\"></sup>that you also may believe.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26850AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26850AZ\"></sup>For these things took place that the Scripture might be fulfilled: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26850BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26850BA\"></sup>“Not one of his bones <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26850BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26850BB\"></sup>will be broken.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And again another Scripture says, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26851BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26851BC\"></sup>“They will look on him whom they have pierced.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26852BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26852BD\"></sup>After these things Joseph of Arimathea, who was a disciple of Jesus, but secretly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26852BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26852BE\"></sup>for fear of the Jews, asked Pilate that he might take away the body of Jesus, and Pilate gave him permission. So he came and took away his body.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26853BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26853BF\"></sup>Nicodemus also, who earlier had come to Jesus by night, came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26853BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26853BG\"></sup>bringing a mixture of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26853BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26853BH\"></sup>myrrh and aloes, about seventy-five pounds in weight.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they took the body of Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26854BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26854BI\"></sup>bound it in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26854BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26854BJ\"></sup>linen cloths with the spices, as is the burial custom of the Jews.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Now in the place where he was crucified there was a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26855BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26855BK\"></sup>garden, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26855BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26855BL\"></sup>in the garden a new tomb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26855BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26855BM\"></sup>in which no one had yet been laid.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>So because of the Jewish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26856BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26856BN\"></sup>day of Preparation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26856BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26856BO\"></sup>since the tomb was close at hand, they laid Jesus there."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26857A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26857A\"></sup>Now on the first day of the week Mary Magdalene came to the tomb early, while it was still dark, and saw that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26857B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26857B\"></sup>the stone had been taken away from the tomb.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So she ran and went to Simon Peter and the other disciple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26858C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26858C\"></sup>the one whom Jesus loved, and said to them, “They have taken the Lord out of the tomb, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26858D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26858D\"></sup>we do not know where they have laid him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26859E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26859E\"></sup>So Peter went out with the other disciple, and they were going toward the tomb.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Both of them were running together, but the other disciple outran Peter and reached the tomb first.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And stooping to look in, he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26861F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26861F\"></sup>the linen cloths lying there, but he did not go in.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then Simon Peter came, following him, and went into the tomb. He saw the linen cloths lying there,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26863G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26863G\"></sup>the face cloth, which had been on Jesus' head, not lying with the linen cloths but folded up in a place by itself.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the other disciple, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26864H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26864H\"></sup>who had reached the tomb first, also went in, and he saw and believed;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>for as yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26865I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26865I\"></sup>they did not understand the Scripture, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26865J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26865J\"></sup>that he must rise from the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the disciples went back to their homes.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But Mary stood weeping outside the tomb, and as she wept she stooped to look into the tomb.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26868K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26868K\"></sup>she saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26868L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26868L\"></sup>two angels in white, sitting where the body of Jesus had lain, one at the head and one at the feet.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They said to her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26869M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26869M\"></sup>“Woman, why are you weeping?” She said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26869N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26869N\"></sup>“They have taken away my Lord, and I do not know where they have laid him.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Having said this, she turned around and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26870O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26870O\"></sup>saw Jesus standing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26870P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26870P\"></sup>but she did not know that it was Jesus.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26871Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26871Q\"></sup>“Woman, why are you weeping? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26871R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26871R\"></sup>Whom are you seeking?”</span> Supposing him to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26871S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26871S\"></sup>the gardener, she said to him, “Sir, if you have carried him away, tell me where you have laid him, and I will take him away.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Mary.”</span> She turned and said to him in Aramaic, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26872T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26872T\"></sup>“Rabboni!” (which means Teacher).",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“Do not cling to me, for I have not yet ascended to the Father; but go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26873U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26873U\"></sup>my brothers and say to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26873V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26873V\"></sup>‘I am ascending to my Father and your Father, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26873W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26873W\"></sup>my God and your God.’”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Mary Magdalene <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26874X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26874X\"></sup>went and announced to the disciples, “I have seen the Lord”—and that he had said these things to her.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26875Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26875Y\"></sup>On the evening <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26875Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26875Z\"></sup>of that day, the first day of the week, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26875AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26875AA\"></sup>the doors being locked where the disciples were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26875AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26875AB\"></sup>for fear of the Jews, Jesus came and stood among them and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26875AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26875AC\"></sup>“Peace be with you.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When he had said this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26876AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26876AD\"></sup>he showed them his hands and his side. Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26876AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26876AE\"></sup>the disciples were glad when they saw the Lord.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus said to them again, <span class=\"woj\">“Peace be with you. As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26877AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26877AF\"></sup>the Father has sent me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26877AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26877AG\"></sup>even so I am sending you.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And when he had said this, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26878AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26878AH\"></sup>breathed on them and said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26878AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26878AI\"></sup>“Receive the Holy Spirit.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26879AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26879AJ\"></sup>If you forgive the sins of any, they are forgiven them; if you withhold forgiveness from any, it is withheld.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26880AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26880AK\"></sup>Thomas, one of the twelve, called the Twin, was not with them when Jesus came.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So the other disciples told him, “We have seen the Lord.” But he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26881AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26881AL\"></sup>“Unless I see in his hands the mark of the nails, and place my finger into the mark of the nails, and place my hand into his side, I will never believe.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Eight days later, his disciples were inside again, and Thomas was with them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26882AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26882AM\"></sup>Although the doors were locked, Jesus came and stood among them and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26882AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26882AN\"></sup>“Peace be with you.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then he said to Thomas, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26883AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26883AO\"></sup>“Put your finger here, and see my hands; and put out your hand, and place it in my side. Do not disbelieve, but believe.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Thomas answered him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26884AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26884AP\"></sup>“My Lord and my God!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you believed because you have seen me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26885AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26885AQ\"></sup>Blessed are those who have not seen and yet have believed.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26886AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26886AR\"></sup>Now Jesus did many other signs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26886AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26886AS\"></sup>in the presence of the disciples, which are not written in this book;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26887AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26887AT\"></sup>but these are written so that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26887AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26887AU\"></sup>believe that Jesus is the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26887AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26887AV\"></sup>the Son of God, and that by believing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26887AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26887AW\"></sup>you may have life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26887AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26887AX\"></sup>in his name."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>After this Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26888A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26888A\"></sup>revealed himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26888B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26888B\"></sup>again to the disciples by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26888C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26888C\"></sup>the Sea of Tiberias, and he revealed himself in this way.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Simon Peter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26889D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26889D\"></sup>Thomas (called the Twin), Nathanael of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26889E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26889E\"></sup>Cana in Galilee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26889F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26889F\"></sup>the sons of Zebedee, and two others of his disciples were together.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Simon Peter said to them, “I am going fishing.” They said to him, “We will go with you.” They went out and got into the boat, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26890G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26890G\"></sup>that night they caught nothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Just as day was breaking, Jesus stood on the shore; yet the disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26891H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26891H\"></sup>did not know that it was Jesus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26892I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26892I\"></sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Children, do you have any fish?”</span> They answered him, “No.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26893J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26893J\"></sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Cast the net on the right side of the boat, and you will find some.”</span> So they cast it, and now they were not able to haul it in, because of the quantity of fish.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>That disciple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26894K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26894K\"></sup>whom Jesus loved therefore said to Peter, “It is the Lord!” When Simon Peter heard that it was the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26894L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26894L\"></sup>he put on his outer garment, for he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26894M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26894M\"></sup>stripped for work, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26894N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26894N\"></sup>threw himself into the sea.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The other disciples came in the boat, dragging the net full of fish, for they were not far from the land, but about a hundred yards off.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When they got out on land, they saw a charcoal fire in place, with fish laid out on it, and bread.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Bring some of the fish that you have just caught.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So Simon Peter went aboard and hauled the net ashore, full of large fish, 153 of them. And although there were so many, the net was not torn.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26899O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26899O\"></sup>“Come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26899P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26899P\"></sup>have breakfast.”</span> Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26899Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26899Q\"></sup>none of the disciples dared ask him, “Who are you?” They knew it was the Lord.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Jesus came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26900R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26900R\"></sup>took the bread and gave it to them, and so with the fish.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26901S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26901S\"></sup>This was now the third time that Jesus was revealed to the disciples after he was raised from the dead.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26902T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26902T\"></sup>finished breakfast, Jesus said to Simon Peter, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26902U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26902U\"></sup>“Simon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26902V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26902V\"></sup>son of John, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26902W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26902W\"></sup>do you love me more than these?”</span> He said to him, “Yes, Lord; you know that I love you.” He said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Feed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26902X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26902X\"></sup>my lambs.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He said to him a second time, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, son of John, do you love me?”</span> He said to him, “Yes, Lord; you know that I love you.” He said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26903Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26903Y\"></sup>“Tend <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26903Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26903Z\"></sup>my sheep.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He said to him the third time, <span class=\"woj\">“Simon, son of John, do you love me?”</span> Peter was grieved because he said to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26904AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26904AA\"></sup>the third time, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you love me?”</span> and he said to him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26904AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26904AB\"></sup>you know everything; you know that I love you.” Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Feed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26904AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26904AC\"></sup>my sheep.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26905AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26905AD\"></sup>Truly, truly, I say to you, when you were young, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26905AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26905AE\"></sup>you used to dress yourself and walk wherever you wanted, but when you are old, you will stretch out your hands, and another will dress you and carry you where you do not want to go.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>(This he said to show <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26906AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26906AF\"></sup>by what kind of death he was to glorify God.) And after saying this he said to him, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26906AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26906AG\"></sup>“Follow me.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Peter turned and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26907AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26907AH\"></sup>the disciple whom Jesus loved following them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26907AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26907AI\"></sup>the one who also had leaned back against him during the supper and had said, “Lord, who is it that is going to betray you?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When Peter saw him, he said to Jesus, “Lord, what about this man?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“If it is my will that he remain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26909AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26909AJ\"></sup>until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26909AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26909AK\"></sup>I come, what is that to you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26909AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26909AL\"></sup>You follow me!”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So the saying spread abroad among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26910AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26910AM\"></sup>the brothers that this disciple was not to die; yet Jesus did not say to him that he was not to die, but, <span class=\"woj\">“If it is my will that he remain until I come, what is that to you?”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>This is the disciple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26911AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26911AN\"></sup>who is bearing witness about these things, and who has written these things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26911AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26911AO\"></sup>we know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26911AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26911AP\"></sup>that his testimony is true.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26912AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26912AQ\"></sup>there are also many other things that Jesus did. Were every one of them to be written, I suppose that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26912AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26912AR\"></sup>the world itself could not contain the books that would be written."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;